WEBVTT

1
00:00:06.000 --> 00:00:12.074
Support us and become VIP member 
to remove all ads from www.OpenSubtitles.org

2
00:00:34.897 --> 00:00:38.765
<b>-[ Thunder Rumbling ]
-[ Baby Crying ]</b>

3
00:00:50.046 --> 00:00:52.514
<b>-[ Woman #1 ] Is it a girl?
-[ Woman #2 ] Yes.</b>

4
00:00:52.582 --> 00:00:54.311
<b>[ Woman #1 ]
Show me its arm.</b>

5
00:00:54.383 --> 00:00:57.284
<b>- [ Woman #2 ] She bears the mark.
- [ Woman #3 ] No!</b>

6
00:00:57.353 --> 00:00:59.844
<b>-[ Sobbing ]
-[ Baby Crying ]</b>

7
00:00:59.922 --> 00:01:03.449
<b>The omen is true.
I must tell my mother.</b>

8
00:01:05.862 --> 00:01:07.989
<b>- [ Sobbing ] Help me!
- [ Woman #2 ] I can't.</b>

9
00:01:08.064 --> 00:01:10.862
<b>- They're going to kill her.
- [ Baby's Cries Continue ]</b>

10
00:01:18.775 --> 00:01:23.303
<b>[ Mother. Sobbing ]
Oh. thank you. Ethna. Thank you.</b>

11
00:01:31.821 --> 00:01:34.381
<b>[ Guard ]
Stand aside for Queen Bavmorda!</b>

12
00:01:42.999 --> 00:01:45.126
<b>[ Barking. Snarling ]</b>

13
00:01:58.748 --> 00:02:01.239
<b>You cannot
stop the prophecy!</b>

14
00:02:01.317 --> 00:02:04.252
<b>This child will have no power over me.
Start the ritual.</b>

15
00:02:04.320 --> 00:02:09.189
<b>- No. No!
- Where's the baby?</b>

16
00:02:09.258 --> 00:02:11.692
<b>The midwife.
Find that baby. Sorsha.</b>

17
00:02:11.761 --> 00:02:15.128
<b>Use the dogs.
Bring her back to me alive!</b>

18
00:02:15.198 --> 00:02:17.325
<b>Your reign of terror
is at an end!</b>

19
00:02:17.400 --> 00:02:19.493
<b>She will come back.
and she will finish you!</b>

20
00:02:19.569 --> 00:02:23.162
<b>- [ Guard ] Silence. wench.
- My baby will finish you!
- Kill her.</b>

21
00:03:29.028 --> 00:03:33.431
<b>[ Barking. Howling ]</b>

22
00:03:41.708 --> 00:03:46.077
<b>[ Barks. Howls Continue ]</b>

23
00:04:01.394 --> 00:04:05.228
<b>[ Gasping. Panting ]</b>

24
00:04:05.932 --> 00:04:09.390
<b>[ Dog Bellowing ]</b>

25
00:04:09.469 --> 00:04:11.460
<b>[ Baby Crying ]</b>

26
00:04:16.009 --> 00:04:21.276
<b>[ Barking Continues ]</b>

27
00:05:18.171 --> 00:05:20.162
<b>[ Cooing ]</b>

28
00:05:33.269 --> 00:05:35.737
<b>[ Bird Twittering ]</b>

29
00:05:39.342 --> 00:05:41.276
<b>[ Coos ]</b>

30
00:05:50.353 --> 00:05:52.344
<b>Dada! Dada!</b>

31
00:05:55.758 --> 00:05:59.057
<b>-Dada! Dada!
- Whoa! Whoa!</b>

32
00:06:00.329 --> 00:06:03.560
<b>Dada! Dada!
We found something in the river.</b>

33
00:06:03.633 --> 00:06:05.567
<b>I can't run off and play
with you now. Ranon.</b>

34
00:06:05.635 --> 00:06:07.933
<b>- I've got work to do.
- You gotta come. Hurry!</b>

35
00:06:09.438 --> 00:06:11.429
<b>[ Chuckles ]</b>

36
00:06:12.909 --> 00:06:15.469
<b>Come on.</b>

37
00:06:17.813 --> 00:06:20.839
<b>Don't go near it.
We don't know where it's been.</b>

38
00:06:20.917 --> 00:06:23.852
<b>But. Dada. it's a baby.</b>

39
00:06:23.920 --> 00:06:28.721
<b>- It's not like us.
- No. It's not a Nelwyn.</b>

40
00:06:28.791 --> 00:06:32.352
<b>- It looks like a Daikini baby.
- What's a Daikini?</b>

41
00:06:32.428 --> 00:06:34.760
<b>Daikinis are big.</b>

42
00:06:34.830 --> 00:06:37.958
<b>- Giants who live far away.
- [ Laughing ]</b>

43
00:06:38.034 --> 00:06:40.332
<b>Oh. she's so cute.</b>

44
00:06:40.403 --> 00:06:44.430
<b>- Can't we keep it. Dada?
- No!</b>

45
00:06:44.507 --> 00:06:49.740
<b>We'll push it downstream and forget
we ever saw it. Come on.</b>

46
00:06:49.812 --> 00:06:51.746
<b>- Come on.
- Ufgood! Willow Ufgood!</b>

47
00:06:51.814 --> 00:06:55.978
<b>Shhh! It's the prefect.
That's all I need.</b>

48
00:06:56.052 --> 00:06:59.510
<b>Keep it quiet.
Don't touch it.</b>

49
00:07:01.057 --> 00:07:04.891
<b>[ Woman ] Mr. Burglekutt. my husband
hasn't stolen anything!</b>

50
00:07:04.961 --> 00:07:06.952
<b>Baaa!</b>

51
00:07:10.366 --> 00:07:13.858
<b>Ufgood. you still haven't
paid your debts to me.</b>

52
00:07:13.936 --> 00:07:15.961
<b>Where did you
get these seeds?</b>

53
00:07:16.038 --> 00:07:18.768
<b>Well. maybe I used magic.</b>

54
00:07:18.841 --> 00:07:22.800
<b>[ Laughs ] You're no sorcerer. Ufgood.
You're a clown.</b>

55
00:07:22.878 --> 00:07:26.439
<b>I sell the planting seeds around here.
Now tell me where you got them.</b>

56
00:07:26.515 --> 00:07:29.973
<b>My family's been gathering them
in the forest since last fall.</b>

57
00:07:30.052 --> 00:07:33.078
<b>- There's no law against that.
- [ Children Laughing ]</b>

58
00:07:33.155 --> 00:07:38.320
<b>Willow. you didn't leave
them alone by the river?</b>

59
00:07:38.394 --> 00:07:40.726
<b>Magic?
You'll need magic...</b>

60
00:07:40.796 --> 00:07:43.162
<b>if you expect to get your planting
done before the rains start.</b>

61
00:07:45.201 --> 00:07:50.730
<b>I will have this land. And you're
gonna end up working in the mines.</b>

62
00:07:52.942 --> 00:07:56.673
<b>- [ Burglekutt ] Baaa--
- [ Hog Snorting ]</b>

63
00:07:59.815 --> 00:08:02.807
<b>[ Giggling ]
Oh. you're lovely.</b>

64
00:08:02.885 --> 00:08:04.876
<b>- Yes. you are.
- [ Coos ]</b>

65
00:08:04.954 --> 00:08:09.391
<b>- Kiaya!
- Oh. Willow!</b>

66
00:08:09.458 --> 00:08:14.395
<b>- Good girl. Good girl.
- Under no condition whatsoever...</b>

67
00:08:14.463 --> 00:08:17.193
<b>is anyone in this family
to fall in love with that baby.</b>

68
00:08:17.266 --> 00:08:21.999
<b>Yes. you are. Come on. Mims.
Come on. Come on.</b>

69
00:08:22.071 --> 00:08:24.130
<b>There we are. Come on.</b>

70
00:08:24.206 --> 00:08:26.834
<b>Hey. I will not be ignored!</b>

71
00:08:26.909 --> 00:08:30.606
<b>Mims? Ranon?</b>

72
00:08:41.590 --> 00:08:43.751
<b>- [ Fussing ]
- You're gonna be all clean.</b>

73
00:08:47.430 --> 00:08:50.331
<b>[ Baby Giggling ]</b>

74
00:08:50.399 --> 00:08:53.698
<b>Willow. do you think we should
take her to the village council?</b>

75
00:08:53.769 --> 00:08:56.363
<b>No. No.
They'll think it's a bad omen.</b>

76
00:08:56.439 --> 00:08:59.272
<b>There'll be a flood or a drought.
and everyone will blame me for it.</b>

77
00:08:59.341 --> 00:09:02.242
<b>''Willow Ufgood brought around
that Daikini. didn't he?</b>

78
00:09:02.311 --> 00:09:05.337
<b>That's right. He's that
lousy farmer too. Let's get him!''</b>

79
00:09:05.414 --> 00:09:09.475
<b>- Willow. calm down.
- Calm down?</b>

80
00:09:09.552 --> 00:09:11.611
<b>Kiaya. tomorrow's my big day.</b>

81
00:09:11.687 --> 00:09:15.418
<b>Love. the High Aldwin hasn't
picked a new apprentice in years.</b>

82
00:09:15.491 --> 00:09:18.790
<b>Tomorrow's gonna be different.
I just know he's gonna pick me.</b>

83
00:09:21.530 --> 00:09:25.193
<b>- Here. Hold her.
- Hey. no. I don't want her. Kiaya.</b>

84
00:09:25.267 --> 00:09:28.065
<b>- Hold her while I get some milk.
- Oh. no. no. Oh.</b>

85
00:09:28.137 --> 00:09:32.870
<b>- [ Giggling ]
- [ Squeals ]</b>

86
00:09:35.711 --> 00:09:39.169
<b>- Dada. she likes you.
- [ Giggles ]</b>

87
00:09:40.950 --> 00:09:46.115
<b>[ Cooing. Laughing ]</b>

88
00:09:46.188 --> 00:09:47.356
<b>-[ Rooster Crowing ]
- Bye.</b>

89
00:09:47.356 --> 00:09:50.450
<b>-[ Rooster Crowing ]
- Bye.</b>

90
00:09:50.526 --> 00:09:54.428
<b>- Come on. kids. Let's go.
- [ Mims Giggling ]</b>

91
00:09:58.134 --> 00:10:00.398
<b>-  [ Festive ]
- [ Villagers Chattering ]</b>

92
00:10:00.469 --> 00:10:04.064
<b>[ Willow ]
I will now magically join the rings!</b>

93
00:10:05.574 --> 00:10:08.407
<b>~~[ Continues ]</b>

94
00:10:26.028 --> 00:10:28.656
<b>- Whoa-ah!
- [ Laughing ]</b>

95
00:10:33.435 --> 00:10:35.835
<b>Thank you. son.</b>

96
00:10:35.905 --> 00:10:40.933
<b>If you're easily shocked.
please turn away.</b>

97
00:10:41.010 --> 00:10:43.069
<b>- [ Gasps ]
- [ Oohing And Aahing ]</b>

98
00:10:44.880 --> 00:10:47.644
<b>~~[ Continues ]</b>

99
00:10:54.123 --> 00:10:56.057
<b>[ Honking ]</b>

100
00:10:56.125 --> 00:10:58.389
<b>Give me a ripe one. Good.</b>

101
00:11:04.600 --> 00:11:09.094
<b>- [ Squeals ]
- And now. for my final amazing feat.</b>

102
00:11:09.171 --> 00:11:14.006
<b>- I will make this entire pig disappear!
- [ Skeptical Groans ]</b>

103
00:11:14.076 --> 00:11:16.544
<b>[ Laughs ]</b>

104
00:11:18.848 --> 00:11:22.011
<b>[ Squealing ]</b>

105
00:11:22.084 --> 00:11:27.215
<b>- Mims. see?
- Please. watch very closely.</b>

106
00:11:27.289 --> 00:11:32.921
<b>- Wuppity bairn. deru. deru!
- [ Surprised Laughter]</b>

107
00:11:35.164 --> 00:11:37.564
<b>- Well--
- What happened to your pig?</b>

108
00:11:37.633 --> 00:11:40.193
<b>- [ Pig Squealing ]
- [ Gasps ]</b>

109
00:11:40.269 --> 00:11:43.329
<b>No!
Hey. come here. you!</b>

110
00:11:47.776 --> 00:11:51.177
<b>I seen enough.
[ Laughing ]</b>

111
00:11:53.148 --> 00:11:56.777
<b>~~[ Fanfare ]</b>

112
00:12:00.789 --> 00:12:03.781
<b>-[ Low. Deep Horn Blows ]
-[ Villagers Chattering ]</b>

113
00:12:06.295 --> 00:12:09.560
<b>Attention!
The High Aldwin...</b>

114
00:12:09.632 --> 00:12:12.567
<b>-will now make his choice
for his new apprentice!
- You'll be all right.</b>

115
00:12:12.635 --> 00:12:16.093
<b>Bring forth the hopefuls.</b>

116
00:12:16.171 --> 00:12:18.571
<b>- Good luck.
- Good luck. Dada.</b>

117
00:12:18.641 --> 00:12:22.407
<b>Willow Ufgood. a hopeful?
How did he get picked?</b>

118
00:12:22.478 --> 00:12:24.969
<b>Is this a joke?
[ Guffaws ]</b>

119
00:12:25.047 --> 00:12:29.507
<b>-[ Burglekutt's Laughing Continues ]
- Willow?</b>

120
00:12:31.939 --> 00:12:37.377
<b>Magic is the bloodstream
of the universe!</b>

121
00:12:37.444 --> 00:12:42.006
<b>Forget all you know...
or think you know.</b>

122
00:12:42.082 --> 00:12:46.109
<b>All that your require
is your intuition.</b>

123
00:12:46.187 --> 00:12:50.283
<b>Now. the power
to control the world...</b>

124
00:12:50.357 --> 00:12:54.851
<b>is in which finger?</b>

125
00:13:36.837 --> 00:13:41.365
<b>- No apprentice this year!
- [ Onlookers Groan ]</b>

126
00:13:41.442 --> 00:13:46.345
<b>~~[ Resumes ]</b>

127
00:13:53.821 --> 00:13:56.813
<b>[ Creature Bellowing ]</b>

128
00:13:57.992 --> 00:14:01.689
<b>- [ Panicked Screams ]
-[ Dog Barks ]</b>

129
00:14:01.762 --> 00:14:05.163
<b>- Where's Mims?
- I don't know. She was right here!</b>

130
00:14:05.232 --> 00:14:08.133
<b>Take Ranon in there. quick!</b>

131
00:14:08.202 --> 00:14:10.466
<b>[ Growling ]</b>

132
00:14:12.106 --> 00:14:14.336
<b>[ Crying ]</b>

133
00:14:16.043 --> 00:14:18.978
<b>- Mims!
- [ Snarling ]</b>

134
00:14:20.347 --> 00:14:22.508
<b>- Mims!
- [ Screaming ]</b>

135
00:14:22.583 --> 00:14:27.020
<b>- [ Crying ]
- [ Snarling ]</b>

136
00:14:28.455 --> 00:14:30.685
<b>- [ Gasps ]
- [ Crying ]</b>

137
00:14:30.758 --> 00:14:35.593
<b>- Mims!
- Dada--</b>

138
00:14:36.864 --> 00:14:39.924
<b>- I'm scared. Dada!
- [ Baby Crying ]</b>

139
00:14:46.640 --> 00:14:50.132
<b>[ Ferocious Growling ]</b>

140
00:14:50.210 --> 00:14:52.804
<b>Come on!</b>

141
00:14:52.880 --> 00:14:55.212
<b>- [ Dog Snarling ]
- [ Yelling ]</b>

142
00:15:10.464 --> 00:15:13.433
<b>- Vohnkar!
- [ Growls ]</b>

143
00:15:13.500 --> 00:15:17.129
<b>- [ Dog Whimpers ]
- [ Men Grunting ]</b>

144
00:15:22.943 --> 00:15:25.844
<b>- Check to make sure.
- It's dead!</b>

145
00:15:28.182 --> 00:15:29.979
<b>Dada! Dada!</b>

146
00:15:33.320 --> 00:15:35.584
<b>It was looking
for somebody's baby!</b>

147
00:15:35.656 --> 00:15:38.523
<b>[ Baby Crying ]</b>

148
00:15:38.592 --> 00:15:42.426
<b>- Mommy.
- Kiaya!</b>

149
00:15:49.803 --> 00:15:53.136
<b>Kiaya!
Kiaya!</b>

150
00:15:53.207 --> 00:15:56.233
<b>- [ Baby Coos ]
- I'm here.</b>

151
00:15:56.310 --> 00:15:58.278
<b>[ Relieved Sigh ]</b>

152
00:16:00.314 --> 00:16:03.943
<b>- Oh. Kiaya.
- [ Baby Fussing ]</b>

153
00:16:04.017 --> 00:16:06.212
<b>We can't keep
the baby. Kiaya.</b>

154
00:16:06.286 --> 00:16:09.153
<b>We have to take her
to the village council.</b>

155
00:16:13.227 --> 00:16:15.923
<b>[ People Chattering ]</b>

156
00:16:22.636 --> 00:16:27.539
<b>Silence! One beast we can kill.
but there may be more.</b>

157
00:16:27.608 --> 00:16:30.008
<b>And you can be assured
that they won't give up...</b>

158
00:16:30.077 --> 00:16:32.045
<b>until they find what
they're looking for!</b>

159
00:16:32.112 --> 00:16:35.377
<b>-[ Man #1 ] It's a sign!
-[ Man #2 ] Who's to blame for this?</b>

160
00:16:35.449 --> 00:16:37.940
<b>[ Man #3 ] We must find the culprit
and throw him in the pit!</b>

161
00:16:38.018 --> 00:16:43.149
<b>- [ Shouting In Agreement ]
- [ Villagers ] In the pit! In the pit!</b>

162
00:16:43.223 --> 00:16:45.350
<b>In the pit! In the pit!</b>

163
00:16:45.426 --> 00:16:48.725
<b>-In the pit! In the pit!
- Willow.</b>

164
00:16:48.796 --> 00:16:53.165
<b>-[ Chanting Continues ]
- Willow Ufgood.</b>

165
00:16:53.233 --> 00:16:55.701
<b>Come forward.</b>

166
00:16:55.769 --> 00:16:59.762
<b>[ Villagers Murmuring ]</b>

167
00:17:01.341 --> 00:17:06.677
<b>My children found this baby
alone by the river. High Aldwin.</b>

168
00:17:08.115 --> 00:17:12.211
<b>[ Crying ]</b>

169
00:17:12.286 --> 00:17:14.447
<b>- A Daikini child.
- [ Villagers Gasping ]</b>

170
00:17:14.521 --> 00:17:17.752
<b>That's what the beasts want.
Let's give it back to them!</b>

171
00:17:17.825 --> 00:17:18.917
<b>[ Villagers ]
Yeah!</b>

172
00:17:18.992 --> 00:17:22.291
<b>- They'll kill her! You can't!
- It isn't one of us.</b>

173
00:17:22.362 --> 00:17:25.024
<b>This child is special!</b>

174
00:17:25.098 --> 00:17:29.398
<b>This child must be taken beyond
the boundaries of our village.</b>

175
00:17:29.470 --> 00:17:32.530
<b>All the way across
the great river...</b>

176
00:17:32.606 --> 00:17:34.699
<b>to the Daikini crossroads.</b>

177
00:17:34.775 --> 00:17:39.474
<b>- Well. who'll do that?
- It seems only fair...</b>

178
00:17:39.546 --> 00:17:42.913
<b>that the man to take
this baby to the crossroads...</b>

179
00:17:42.983 --> 00:17:45.952
<b>be the very man who
plucked it out of the river.</b>

180
00:17:47.521 --> 00:17:50.149
<b>- I nominate Willow Ufgood.
- [ Villagers Shout Agreement ]</b>

181
00:17:50.224 --> 00:17:52.749
<b>No!</b>

182
00:17:52.826 --> 00:17:56.387
<b>I will consult the bones!</b>

183
00:17:57.397 --> 00:17:58.830
<b>[ Fussing ]</b>

184
00:18:03.770 --> 00:18:09.265
<b>- The bones tell me... nothing.
-[ Baby Coos ]</b>

185
00:18:10.911 --> 00:18:14.847
<b>Do you have any love
for this child?</b>

186
00:18:23.257 --> 00:18:27.751
<b>Yes. Yes. I do.</b>

187
00:18:27.828 --> 00:18:32.231
<b>- The bones have spoken!
- [ Villagers Murmuring ]</b>

188
00:18:32.299 --> 00:18:36.258
<b>Willow Ufgood. the safety
of this village depends upon you.</b>

189
00:18:36.336 --> 00:18:40.432
<b>- Praise the bones!
- [ Repeating ] Praise the bones!</b>

190
00:18:40.507 --> 00:18:42.998
<b>[ High Aldwin ]
But you will need help.</b>

191
00:18:43.076 --> 00:18:48.446
<b>Who has the courage to protect
our brave fellow on his journey?</b>

192
00:18:50.484 --> 00:18:54.580
<b>- I'll go with him.
- Ah. Meegosh.</b>

193
00:18:54.655 --> 00:18:57.954
<b>- Excellent choice.
- I'll go!</b>

194
00:18:58.025 --> 00:19:00.493
<b>[ Villagers. Shouting ]
Vohnkar! Vohnkar!</b>

195
00:19:00.561 --> 00:19:03.257
<b>No! Not Vohnkar!
He's the best warrior in the village!</b>

196
00:19:03.330 --> 00:19:06.527
<b>We need him here!
Vohnkar. step back!</b>

197
00:19:14.541 --> 00:19:17.135
<b>All this expedition needs
is a leader.</b>

198
00:19:17.210 --> 00:19:20.577
<b>And according to the bones...</b>

199
00:19:20.647 --> 00:19:24.048
<b>- Eh--
-that leader is...</b>

200
00:19:24.117 --> 00:19:25.549
<b>you. Burglekutt!</b>

201
00:19:25.549 --> 00:19:26.538
<b>you. Burglekutt!</b>

202
00:19:26.617 --> 00:19:30.109
<b>Vohnkar!</b>

203
00:19:30.187 --> 00:19:34.283
<b>- What's your problem. son?
- How do you mean?</b>

204
00:19:34.358 --> 00:19:39.660
<b>When I held up my fingers
what was your first impulse?</b>

205
00:19:39.730 --> 00:19:43.632
<b>- Well. it was stupid.
-Just tell me.</b>

206
00:19:43.701 --> 00:19:48.161
<b>- To pick my own finger.
- Aha! That was the correct answer.</b>

207
00:19:48.239 --> 00:19:52.972
<b>You lack faith in yourself.
More than anyone in the village.</b>

208
00:19:53.044 --> 00:19:55.672
<b>you have the potential
to be a great sorcerer.</b>

209
00:19:55.746 --> 00:20:00.581
<b>Now. when you're out there.
listen to your own heart.</b>

210
00:20:02.520 --> 00:20:07.548
<b>- These will protect you. They're magic!
- Acorns?</b>

211
00:20:07.625 --> 00:20:11.652
<b>Anything you throw them at
turns to stone.</b>

212
00:20:14.699 --> 00:20:17.930
<b>You have much to learn.
young Ufgood.</b>

213
00:20:30.881 --> 00:20:35.341
<b>- Are you scared. Dada?
- No!</b>

214
00:20:35.419 --> 00:20:39.651
<b>Even with fairies in the woods that'll
put you to sleep for a hundred years?</b>

215
00:20:41.659 --> 00:20:43.786
<b>- Doesn't bother me.
- Brownies?</b>

216
00:20:43.861 --> 00:20:46.796
<b>- Dragons?
- Trolls?</b>

217
00:20:46.864 --> 00:20:50.300
<b>Trolls that'll skin you alive
and take your face off?</b>

218
00:20:50.368 --> 00:20:53.997
<b>Ranon!
You know I hate trolls.</b>

219
00:20:54.071 --> 00:20:57.199
<b>I can be your guard
and carry your spear.</b>

220
00:20:57.274 --> 00:20:58.832
<b>Me too. Me too. Dada.</b>

221
00:21:00.444 --> 00:21:05.780
<b>What a lucky father I am. I wish
I could take you bobbins with me.</b>

222
00:21:08.853 --> 00:21:11.413
<b>Good-bye. Dada.</b>

223
00:21:13.457 --> 00:21:17.450
<b>Go play!
Go on.</b>

224
00:21:21.432 --> 00:21:24.959
<b>We've never been apart.</b>

225
00:21:26.003 --> 00:21:29.336
<b>I miss you already.</b>

226
00:21:30.674 --> 00:21:34.110
<b>Don't worry. Kiaya.
I'll be fine.</b>

227
00:21:34.178 --> 00:21:36.112
<b>I'll be back
before you know it.</b>

228
00:21:38.349 --> 00:21:41.079
<b>Well. remember
to keep her warm.</b>

229
00:21:43.120 --> 00:21:45.850
<b>And... here.</b>

230
00:21:47.992 --> 00:21:50.790
<b>This will bring you luck.</b>

231
00:22:03.974 --> 00:22:06.306
<b>Good brave people!</b>

232
00:22:08.145 --> 00:22:10.875
<b>The outer world is
no place for a Nelwyn.</b>

233
00:22:10.948 --> 00:22:15.681
<b>Give the baby to the first
Daikini you see. then hurry home.</b>

234
00:22:19.190 --> 00:22:22.785
<b>Tuatha...
lokwathrak... tuatha!</b>

235
00:22:22.860 --> 00:22:26.387
<b>[ High Aldwin ]
Go in the direction the bird is flying!</b>

236
00:22:26.464 --> 00:22:30.400
<b>- [ Giggling ]
- Ooh.</b>

237
00:22:30.468 --> 00:22:33.301
<b>It's going back to the village!</b>

238
00:22:35.139 --> 00:22:37.130
<b>Ignore the bird.
Follow the river.</b>

239
00:22:37.208 --> 00:22:39.438
<b>Move out!</b>

240
00:23:00.397 --> 00:23:03.332
<b>[ Fussing ]</b>

241
00:23:03.400 --> 00:23:06.858
<b>- Hold on. Meegosh.
- What's wrong?</b>

242
00:23:06.937 --> 00:23:10.964
<b>- We have to stop.
- Stop? Why?</b>

243
00:23:11.041 --> 00:23:13.509
<b>- The baby's sick.
- [ Bawling ]</b>

244
00:23:17.481 --> 00:23:22.077
<b>She's not sick!
Let me see.</b>

245
00:23:22.153 --> 00:23:25.350
<b>Uhaghh!
Take her! Take her!</b>

246
00:23:25.422 --> 00:23:27.890
<b>-[ Burglekutt's Groans Continue ]
- [ Laughing ]</b>

247
00:23:27.958 --> 00:23:31.018
<b>She'll be fine
once she gets some rest.</b>

248
00:23:31.095 --> 00:23:33.290
<b>[ Cooing ]</b>

249
00:23:33.364 --> 00:23:35.059
<b>[ Groaning ]
Clean me up.</b>

250
00:23:38.702 --> 00:23:41.933
<b>[ Bavmorda ] I didn't ask you
to bring me a dead nursemaid.</b>

251
00:23:42.006 --> 00:23:45.908
<b>-Sorsha. you're useless!
-I'm backtracking the nursemaid's trail.</b>

252
00:23:45.976 --> 00:23:48.171
<b>I'll find where
she hid the baby.</b>

253
00:23:50.147 --> 00:23:52.411
<b>Ah. General Kael. at last.</b>

254
00:23:52.483 --> 00:23:57.216
<b>My queen. I have destroyed
the castle at Galladoorn.</b>

255
00:23:57.288 --> 00:24:00.985
<b>Well done. But now I have
another task for you.</b>

256
00:24:01.058 --> 00:24:06.519
<b>Help my daughter to find
that tiny. helpless baby...</b>

257
00:24:06.597 --> 00:24:08.588
<b>that continues
somehow to elude her.</b>

258
00:24:10.501 --> 00:24:12.469
<b>The baby of the prophecy?</b>

259
00:24:12.536 --> 00:24:15.972
<b>- The one that would destroy you?
- I need that baby alive.</b>

260
00:24:16.040 --> 00:24:18.508
<b>I must perform
the ritual that will...</b>

261
00:24:18.576 --> 00:24:21.943
<b>exile the child's spirit
into oblivion.</b>

262
00:24:22.012 --> 00:24:24.742
<b>- Find her!
- I don't need his help. Mother.</b>

263
00:24:24.815 --> 00:24:26.874
<b>You'll do as I say. child.</b>

264
00:24:33.324 --> 00:24:35.485
<b>I read the signs.</b>

265
00:24:35.559 --> 00:24:38.756
<b>One day. I fear. your daughter
will betray you.</b>

266
00:24:38.829 --> 00:24:42.993
<b>I trust her loyalty
more than I trust yours.</b>

267
00:24:47.938 --> 00:24:53.740
<b>[ Baby Cooing ]</b>

268
00:24:53.811 --> 00:24:55.802
<b>- [ Squealing ]
-[ Dogs Barking. Men Shouting ]</b>

269
00:24:58.716 --> 00:25:01.276
<b>- Move!
-[ Baby Fussing ]</b>

270
00:25:01.352 --> 00:25:03.286
<b>It's an ambush.
Come on. Move!</b>

271
00:25:03.354 --> 00:25:07.518
<b>-[ Dogs Barking ]
- [ Horses Neighing ]</b>

272
00:25:07.591 --> 00:25:11.322
<b>- Come on!
- [ Dogs Snarling ]</b>

273
00:25:20.904 --> 00:25:23.839
<b>The Nelwyns have got the baby.
We've searched the village.</b>

274
00:25:23.907 --> 00:25:26.876
<b>But a group of them
are on the road somewhere.</b>

275
00:25:26.944 --> 00:25:28.775
<b>They couldn't have gone far!</b>

276
00:25:28.846 --> 00:25:31.815
<b>Widen the search
and report to Sorsha!</b>

277
00:25:33.050 --> 00:25:36.816
<b>- [ Dog Barks Fading ]
- [ Sputtering Sigh ]</b>

278
00:25:39.223 --> 00:25:41.919
<b>Come. We'll keep to the woods.</b>

279
00:26:20.698 --> 00:26:24.896
<b>That's it!
It's the crossroads!</b>

280
00:26:26.904 --> 00:26:28.963
<b>[ Dogs Howling
In The Distance ]</b>

281
00:26:41.318 --> 00:26:44.261
<b>[ Vohnkar] Keep this fire high.
We don't know what's out there.</b>

282
00:26:44.395 --> 00:26:47.421
<b>[ Whimpers ]</b>

283
00:26:49.800 --> 00:26:52.268
<b>-[ Creature Shrieking ]
- What was that?</b>

284
00:26:53.604 --> 00:26:56.402
<b>Get the spears!</b>

285
00:26:58.943 --> 00:27:01.935
<b>[ Crying ]</b>

286
00:27:07.818 --> 00:27:10.548
<b>- [ Shrieking ]
- [ Gasps ]</b>

287
00:27:12.857 --> 00:27:14.791
<b>- [ Growling ]
- Uhh. Uhh.</b>

288
00:27:14.859 --> 00:27:18.727
<b>Give me some water. peck.
or you die.</b>

289
00:27:18.796 --> 00:27:21.230
<b>Do you understand?</b>

290
00:27:21.298 --> 00:27:23.198
<b>- Water.
- Yeah.</b>

291
00:27:23.267 --> 00:27:25.258
<b>[ Grunts. Groans ]</b>

292
00:27:25.336 --> 00:27:27.327
<b>Hurry up!</b>

293
00:27:31.342 --> 00:27:34.243
<b>Get me some water.
you measly little pecks.</b>

294
00:27:34.311 --> 00:27:37.769
<b>It's a Daikini.
We're in luck.</b>

295
00:27:37.848 --> 00:27:40.282
<b>We can't give her to him!</b>

296
00:27:40.351 --> 00:27:44.310
<b>- Somebody put him there for a reason.
- We've got to get rid of her.</b>

297
00:27:44.388 --> 00:27:46.982
<b>- Those soldiers are after us.
- Shhh.</b>

298
00:27:47.058 --> 00:27:49.925
<b>He's looking right at us.</b>

299
00:27:53.864 --> 00:27:55.832
<b>We've got to give
that baby to somebody.</b>

300
00:27:55.900 --> 00:27:58.767
<b>I'm somebody.</b>

301
00:27:58.836 --> 00:28:03.205
<b>Let me out of here. I'll take care
of the baby. [ Smooching Sounds ]</b>

302
00:28:05.042 --> 00:28:09.638
<b>- I trust him completely.
- But he tried to strangle me.</b>

303
00:28:09.714 --> 00:28:13.650
<b>- I want to go home!
- No. Burglekutt!</b>

304
00:28:13.718 --> 00:28:17.085
<b>- We should wait!
- Are you challenging my authority?</b>

305
00:28:17.154 --> 00:28:20.521
<b>As far as this baby
is concerned... yes.</b>

306
00:28:20.591 --> 00:28:23.617
<b>Don't listen to him. Burglekutt.</b>

307
00:28:23.694 --> 00:28:28.791
<b>Fine. You stay here alone.
but we're going.</b>

308
00:28:28.866 --> 00:28:31.096
<b>That's a bad idea.
Very bad.</b>

309
00:28:31.168 --> 00:28:34.604
<b>- Dangerous out there.
- [ Burglekutt ] Get the gear. men.</b>

310
00:28:34.672 --> 00:28:38.233
<b>- Vohnkar--
- It's not his decision!</b>

311
00:28:38.309 --> 00:28:42.245
<b>Burglekutt. you're troll dung.</b>

312
00:28:42.313 --> 00:28:43.974
<b>Don't let him
talk to you that way.</b>

313
00:28:44.048 --> 00:28:46.141
<b>Listen here. runt.</b>

314
00:28:46.217 --> 00:28:50.210
<b>While you're wasting time here.
your fields aren't getting planted.</b>

315
00:28:50.287 --> 00:28:54.587
<b>- Think about it!
- Burglekutt. I'm gonna--</b>

316
00:28:54.658 --> 00:28:58.025
<b>You're gonna what?</b>

317
00:28:58.095 --> 00:29:01.861
<b>[ Laughs ]</b>

318
00:29:01.932 --> 00:29:04.492
<b>Some day. Burglekutt.
Some day.</b>

319
00:29:04.568 --> 00:29:06.593
<b>Vohnkar. let's go!</b>

320
00:29:10.274 --> 00:29:12.970
<b>Meegosh. are you coming?</b>

321
00:29:15.246 --> 00:29:18.841
<b>- I'm staying.
- [ Laughs ] Come on. men.</b>

322
00:29:18.916 --> 00:29:23.114
<b>Burglekutt. let me out of here.
I'll take care of the baby. I swear.</b>

323
00:29:23.187 --> 00:29:25.849
<b>Just let me out of here.
Please!</b>

324
00:29:25.923 --> 00:29:29.381
<b>Vohnkar. let me borrow that spear...
just for a minute.</b>

325
00:29:29.460 --> 00:29:31.724
<b>Get--
Well. at least get me some water!</b>

326
00:29:31.796 --> 00:29:36.756
<b>Burglekutt. don't leave me alone
with these two! [ Frustrated Grunt ]</b>

327
00:29:36.834 --> 00:29:41.635
<b>- [ Baby Crying ]
- What'll we do now. Willow?</b>

328
00:29:41.705 --> 00:29:44.333
<b>Well. that was really stupid. peck.</b>

329
00:29:44.408 --> 00:29:49.209
<b>- Don't call me a peck.
- Oh. I'm sorry... peck.</b>

330
00:29:49.280 --> 00:29:53.046
<b>- Peck. peck. peck. peck.
- You be careful!</b>

331
00:29:53.117 --> 00:29:56.883
<b>I'm a powerful sorcerer.
See this acorn?</b>

332
00:29:58.322 --> 00:30:02.816
<b>- I'll throw it. and turn you to stone.
- Whoo--</b>

333
00:30:02.893 --> 00:30:04.827
<b>I'm really scared.</b>

334
00:30:04.895 --> 00:30:07.762
<b>No. don't! Don't!</b>

335
00:30:07.832 --> 00:30:10.665
<b>There's a peck here
with an acorn pointed at me!</b>

336
00:30:10.734 --> 00:30:13.396
<b>Oh. I wouldn't
want to waste it.</b>

337
00:30:13.470 --> 00:30:16.735
<b>Ha!
Peck. peck. peck. peck.</b>

338
00:30:16.807 --> 00:30:19.367
<b>peck. peck. peck.
peck. peck!</b>

339
00:30:19.443 --> 00:30:21.741
<b>[ Insects Twittering ]</b>

340
00:30:45.035 --> 00:30:47.902
<b>[ Neighing ]</b>

341
00:30:47.972 --> 00:30:50.873
<b>- [ Both Grunting ]
- [ Meegosh ] What was that?</b>

342
00:30:54.245 --> 00:30:57.942
<b>Mornin'. boys.</b>

343
00:30:58.015 --> 00:31:02.145
<b>Rough night last night.
wasn't it?</b>

344
00:31:02.219 --> 00:31:05.586
<b>I don't think I introduced
myself yesterday.</b>

345
00:31:05.656 --> 00:31:09.114
<b>My name is Mad-Martigan.
and you are. uh--</b>

346
00:31:09.193 --> 00:31:12.162
<b>No. Meegosh.
Don't go near him.</b>

347
00:31:12.229 --> 00:31:15.665
<b>- He's dangerous.
- I am not.</b>

348
00:31:15.733 --> 00:31:17.894
<b>Good.</b>

349
00:31:22.640 --> 00:31:24.938
<b>Stop! Wait!</b>

350
00:31:26.677 --> 00:31:29.441
<b>- [ Horse Neighing ]
- Whoa!</b>

351
00:31:29.513 --> 00:31:32.641
<b>- [ Chuckles ]
- [ Horse Gallops Past ]</b>

352
00:31:34.885 --> 00:31:39.413
<b>- What's going on?
- Smells like a battle.</b>

353
00:31:39.490 --> 00:31:42.015
<b>I suppose you're a warrior.</b>

354
00:31:42.092 --> 00:31:44.583
<b>I am the greatest swordsman
that ever lived.</b>

355
00:31:44.662 --> 00:31:47.495
<b>Hmph.</b>

356
00:31:47.564 --> 00:31:51.330
<b>Say. uh-- Could I have
some of that water?</b>

357
00:31:52.336 --> 00:31:54.998
<b>[ Sips Noisily ]</b>

358
00:31:57.374 --> 00:32:00.969
<b>[ Sobbing ]</b>

359
00:32:01.045 --> 00:32:05.812
<b>I don't know why I try.
[ Sobbing ]</b>

360
00:32:10.587 --> 00:32:13.852
<b>I guess I am gonna die here.
Who cares.</b>

361
00:32:13.924 --> 00:32:15.858
<b>- Here.
- Thanks. friend. Oh!</b>

362
00:32:15.926 --> 00:32:18.326
<b>- [ Distant Rumbling ]
- What's that?</b>

363
00:32:18.395 --> 00:32:22.354
<b>[ Mad-Martigan ] I'd say
two or three hundred horses.</b>

364
00:32:22.433 --> 00:32:26.392
<b>five or six wagons...
and about a thousand fools.</b>

365
00:32:26.470 --> 00:32:29.064
<b>[ Mad-Martigan Grunting ]</b>

366
00:32:29.139 --> 00:32:32.905
<b>- Thank you. Ohh--
- Come on. Meegosh.</b>

367
00:32:32.977 --> 00:32:35.673
<b>[ Panting ]</b>

368
00:32:37.247 --> 00:32:40.978
<b>[ Willow ] It's gonna be
all right. little bobbin.</b>

369
00:32:41.051 --> 00:32:43.542
<b>[ Drums Beating ]</b>

370
00:32:46.924 --> 00:32:50.860
<b>- [ Fussing ]
- Everything's gonna be all right.</b>

371
00:32:50.928 --> 00:32:54.125
<b>[ Drumbeats Continue ]</b>

372
00:32:54.198 --> 00:32:57.292
<b>- Excuse me. sir.
- Out of the way. peck!</b>

373
00:32:59.236 --> 00:33:01.602
<b>Uh. pardon me.</b>

374
00:33:01.672 --> 00:33:03.765
<b>Uh--</b>

375
00:33:03.841 --> 00:33:09.336
<b>[ Drumbeats Continue ]</b>

376
00:33:09.413 --> 00:33:14.646
<b>Excuse me. sir. We found one
of your babies in our village.</b>

377
00:33:14.718 --> 00:33:17.619
<b>Will you please
take care of her?</b>

378
00:33:17.688 --> 00:33:22.125
<b>We're going into battle. little ones.
Find a woman to take care of her.</b>

379
00:33:23.560 --> 00:33:26.723
<b>They thought you were
a woman. Airk.</b>

380
00:33:26.797 --> 00:33:29.197
<b>Well--
[ Laughs ]</b>

381
00:33:29.266 --> 00:33:33.828
<b>-Mad-Martigan. what did you do this time?
-Nothing you wouldn't have done.</b>

382
00:33:33.904 --> 00:33:36.270
<b>I always knew
you'd end up in a crow's cage.</b>

383
00:33:36.340 --> 00:33:38.205
<b>At least I'm not
down there herding sheep.</b>

384
00:33:38.275 --> 00:33:39.765
<b>What are you doing this far north?</b>

385
00:33:39.843 --> 00:33:41.868
<b>The Nockmaar army
destroyed Galladoorn.</b>

386
00:33:42.880 --> 00:33:44.177
<b>The castle?</b>

387
00:33:44.248 --> 00:33:46.716
<b>Bavmorda's troops are
crushing everything in sight.</b>

388
00:33:46.784 --> 00:33:48.718
<b>Come on.
Let me out of here. Airk.</b>

389
00:33:48.786 --> 00:33:51.022
<b>Give me a sword.
I'll win this war for you.</b>

390
00:33:51.156 --> 00:33:55.456
<b>Mad-Martigan--
I still serve Galladoorn.</b>

391
00:33:55.527 --> 00:33:57.518
<b>You serve no one.</b>

392
00:33:57.596 --> 00:33:59.826
<b>Remember?</b>

393
00:33:59.898 --> 00:34:03.129
<b>Sit in your coffin and rot.</b>

394
00:34:03.201 --> 00:34:06.261
<b>- Hyah!
- Wait. Airk. You need me!</b>

395
00:34:06.338 --> 00:34:08.772
<b>I'll be around
long after you're dead!</b>

396
00:34:08.840 --> 00:34:11.468
<b>When I get out of here.
I'm gonna cut your head off...</b>

397
00:34:11.543 --> 00:34:13.636
<b>and stick it
on a pig pole!</b>

398
00:34:13.712 --> 00:34:15.737
<b>[ Baby Cooing ]</b>

399
00:34:31.163 --> 00:34:35.896
<b>- [ Fussing ]
- I miss Kiaya and the bobbins.</b>

400
00:34:39.871 --> 00:34:43.671
<b>We're running out of food.</b>

401
00:34:43.742 --> 00:34:47.371
<b>Nobody's gonna
take care of that baby.</b>

402
00:34:47.446 --> 00:34:50.415
<b>You know why?
Nobody cares.</b>

403
00:34:53.318 --> 00:34:56.845
<b>Except me.</b>

404
00:34:56.922 --> 00:35:01.154
<b>You want to go back to your families.
I want out of this cage.</b>

405
00:35:01.226 --> 00:35:05.185
<b>Let me take care of that baby.
I'll look after her like she was my own.</b>

406
00:35:05.263 --> 00:35:08.255
<b>I believe he would. Willow.</b>

407
00:35:08.333 --> 00:35:10.858
<b>He doesn't know
anything about babies.</b>

408
00:35:10.936 --> 00:35:16.169
<b>Right. But I know
a lot of women who do.</b>

409
00:35:16.241 --> 00:35:19.176
<b>If I had somebody in my life.</b>

410
00:35:19.244 --> 00:35:22.839
<b>a little daughter. perhaps.</b>

411
00:35:22.914 --> 00:35:26.179
<b>I might have a reason
to go on living.</b>

412
00:35:29.421 --> 00:35:32.219
<b>You can't leave me
in here to die.</b>

413
00:35:32.290 --> 00:35:35.350
<b>Not when all I want
to do is protect her.</b>

414
00:35:35.427 --> 00:35:38.260
<b>[ Cooing ]</b>

415
00:35:42.300 --> 00:35:44.996
<b>[ Yells. Laughs ]</b>

416
00:35:48.673 --> 00:35:52.575
<b>I feel better!
[ Laughs ]</b>

417
00:35:52.644 --> 00:35:56.375
<b>-You've done the right thing! [ Whoops ]
-Okay. All right. All right.</b>

418
00:35:56.448 --> 00:36:00.908
<b>- You gotta promise to feed her.
- Come to Daddy. little darlin'.</b>

419
00:36:00.986 --> 00:36:06.014
<b>- And keep her clean.
- Absolutely.</b>

420
00:36:06.091 --> 00:36:08.150
<b>- [ Mad-Martigan ] Hee. hee. hee!
-[ Baby Giggling ]</b>

421
00:36:08.226 --> 00:36:13.095
<b>- Wheee!
- [ Baby Squeals ]</b>

422
00:36:13.164 --> 00:36:16.429
<b>She likes me.</b>

423
00:36:16.501 --> 00:36:18.435
<b>[ Giggles ]</b>

424
00:36:18.503 --> 00:36:20.903
<b>Here are her changing rags.</b>

425
00:36:20.972 --> 00:36:23.167
<b>- And her milk bladder.
- Any milk in there?</b>

426
00:36:23.241 --> 00:36:27.507
<b>- It's for her!
- I wouldn't steal from a baby.</b>

427
00:36:29.247 --> 00:36:32.774
<b>- [ Cooing ]
- You worry too much. peck.</b>

428
00:36:32.851 --> 00:36:36.787
<b>- It's Willow.
- I mean Willow.</b>

429
00:36:36.855 --> 00:36:42.623
<b>Now listen. boys-- Willow.
You've done the right thing.</b>

430
00:36:42.694 --> 00:36:46.095
<b>And I want you to get home
and bring your crop in.</b>

431
00:36:52.604 --> 00:36:56.836
<b>- Good-bye. little one.
-[ Cooing ]</b>

432
00:37:05.550 --> 00:37:07.814
<b>Please. take good care of her.</b>

433
00:37:09.588 --> 00:37:12.455
<b>I give you my word of honor!</b>

434
00:37:19.130 --> 00:37:23.032
<b>- Meegosh. slow down!
- Oh. come on!</b>

435
00:37:23.101 --> 00:37:27.333
<b>If we hurry. we can be home by
tomorrow morning. We'll be heroes.</b>

436
00:37:27.405 --> 00:37:30.932
<b>- Do you really think so?
- Sure.</b>

437
00:37:31.009 --> 00:37:33.273
<b>''Look. there's
Willow and Meegosh.</b>

438
00:37:33.345 --> 00:37:35.575
<b>The heroes have come home.''</b>

439
00:37:35.647 --> 00:37:38.741
<b>''Welcome back. boys.
You deserve medals!''</b>

440
00:37:38.817 --> 00:37:43.049
<b>- Yeah. Medals.
- [ Both Laughing ]</b>

441
00:37:43.121 --> 00:37:46.852
<b>Meegosh--</b>

442
00:37:48.727 --> 00:37:52.857
<b>- Did we do the right thing?
- Absolutely.</b>

443
00:37:52.931 --> 00:37:57.231
<b>- There's nothing to worry about.
- [ Baby Crying ]</b>

444
00:38:00.238 --> 00:38:02.536
<b>Hyah! Ha ha!</b>

445
00:38:02.607 --> 00:38:07.840
<b>I stole the baby! I stole the baby!
[ Laughs ]</b>

446
00:38:07.912 --> 00:38:11.678
<b>- Hyah!
- That's my baby!</b>

447
00:38:11.750 --> 00:38:13.718
<b>- Stop! Wait! Come back!
-[ Baby Crying ]</b>

448
00:38:13.785 --> 00:38:16.948
<b>Left. you stupid bird.
Left! Ha ha!</b>

449
00:38:19.758 --> 00:38:23.023
<b>- Ah!
- Ow!</b>

450
00:38:23.094 --> 00:38:26.791
<b>Brownies!
Let's get out of here!</b>

451
00:38:26.865 --> 00:38:30.198
<b>- Come on. Meegosh!
- Ow!</b>

452
00:38:31.202 --> 00:38:34.933
<b>- Uhh-uh-huh-uh.
- Uhh. Oww!</b>

453
00:38:36.241 --> 00:38:38.300
<b>We'll outrun 'em!</b>

454
00:38:38.376 --> 00:38:41.243
<b>- [ Both Yelling ]
-[ Laughing ]</b>

455
00:38:43.048 --> 00:38:47.144
<b>-Hey. ugly. wake up! [ Laughing ]
- [ Gasps ]</b>

456
00:38:47.218 --> 00:38:49.652
<b>Huh?</b>

457
00:38:49.721 --> 00:38:54.818
<b>- [ Grunts. Groans ]
- Stand your ground. He's our prisoner.</b>

458
00:38:54.893 --> 00:38:57.657
<b>Meegosh.
where's the baby?</b>

459
00:38:57.729 --> 00:38:59.663
<b>[ Woman's Voice ]
Bring the Nelwyns to me.</b>

460
00:38:59.731 --> 00:39:01.130
<b>All right. you heard her!</b>

461
00:39:01.199 --> 00:39:04.999
<b>- What's going on?
- Shut up. or I'll break your nose.</b>

462
00:39:05.070 --> 00:39:07.436
<b>You are mine to toy with.</b>

463
00:39:07.505 --> 00:39:11.032
<b>Forward!</b>

464
00:39:11.109 --> 00:39:14.909
<b>- Gimme the rope.
- [ All Grunting ]</b>

465
00:39:14.979 --> 00:39:19.006
<b>Where--
Where...</b>

466
00:39:19.084 --> 00:39:21.348
<b>did you get that baby?</b>

467
00:39:21.419 --> 00:39:26.152
<b>I stole it from a stupid Daikini.
[ Laughs ]</b>

468
00:39:26.324 --> 00:39:29.487
<b>[ Woman ]
Franjean. release the Nelwyns.</b>

469
00:39:29.561 --> 00:39:33.827
<b>-And stop pestering them.
- Uh-oh.</b>

470
00:39:33.898 --> 00:39:35.991
<b>Ahh--</b>

471
00:39:36.067 --> 00:39:38.194
<b>[ Muttering ]</b>

472
00:39:38.269 --> 00:39:40.203
<b>- [ Rope Pops ]
- Yaah!</b>

473
00:39:40.271 --> 00:39:44.401
<b>[ Grunting ]</b>

474
00:39:44.476 --> 00:39:47.707
<b>- You!
- [ Shouting. Laughing ]</b>

475
00:39:47.779 --> 00:39:52.876
<b>Welcome to my kingdom.</b>

476
00:39:52.951 --> 00:39:56.148
<b>- [ Wings Fluttering ]
- [ Kisses. Buzzes ]</b>

477
00:39:59.023 --> 00:40:03.551
<b>- I'm happy to meet you. Willow Ufgood.
- How do you know my name?</b>

478
00:40:03.628 --> 00:40:06.859
<b>Elora Danan told me.</b>

479
00:40:06.931 --> 00:40:10.230
<b>Elora?
Elora. Willow is here.</b>

480
00:40:13.037 --> 00:40:18.600
<b>- But she's just a baby.
- She's very special.</b>

481
00:40:18.676 --> 00:40:24.012
<b>My Brownies have been searching for her
ever since we heard she was born.</b>

482
00:40:24.082 --> 00:40:29.019
<b>Elora Danan has chosen you
to be her guardian.</b>

483
00:40:29.087 --> 00:40:33.854
<b>- Me?
- Yes. She likes you.</b>

484
00:40:35.260 --> 00:40:40.220
<b>And Elora Danan knows you
have the courage to help us.</b>

485
00:40:40.298 --> 00:40:43.893
<b>Take my wand
to the sorceress. Fin Raziel.</b>

486
00:40:43.968 --> 00:40:48.234
<b>She will guide you and Elora Danan
to the kingdom of Tir-Asleen.</b>

487
00:40:48.306 --> 00:40:51.400
<b>where a good king and queen
will look after her.</b>

488
00:40:51.476 --> 00:40:55.275
<b>You need a warrior for
a job like this. I'm a nobody.</b>

489
00:40:55.409 --> 00:40:58.674
<b>Elora. you don't want me.</b>

490
00:40:58.746 --> 00:41:02.477
<b>Tell her.
I'm short. even for a Nelwyn.</b>

491
00:41:05.419 --> 00:41:08.047
<b>Hello?</b>

492
00:41:15.396 --> 00:41:18.797
<b>Elora Danan must survive!</b>

493
00:41:18.866 --> 00:41:23.735
<b>She must fulfill her destiny and bring
about the downfall of Queen Bavmorda.</b>

494
00:41:23.804 --> 00:41:26.637
<b>whose powers are growing
like an evil plague.</b>

495
00:41:26.707 --> 00:41:31.076
<b>Unless she is stopped.
Bavmorda will control the lives...</b>

496
00:41:31.145 --> 00:41:35.707
<b>of your village.
your children-- everyone.</b>

497
00:41:40.387 --> 00:41:43.879
<b>All creatures of good heart
need your help. Willow.</b>

498
00:41:43.957 --> 00:41:49.190
<b>The choice is yours.</b>

499
00:41:49.263 --> 00:41:53.597
<b>[ Thunder Crackling.
Wind Whistling ]</b>

500
00:42:11.752 --> 00:42:15.984
<b>- Hey. Meegosh. Wake up.
- Huh?</b>

501
00:42:16.056 --> 00:42:20.288
<b>- It's time to go home.
- Home?</b>

502
00:42:22.863 --> 00:42:26.424
<b>Listen. Meegosh.
Tell Kiaya I love her.</b>

503
00:42:26.500 --> 00:42:31.062
<b>- And I think of her every day.
- Willow--</b>

504
00:42:31.138 --> 00:42:34.596
<b>And tell her I'm not going to let
anything happen to the baby.</b>

505
00:42:34.675 --> 00:42:37.303
<b>Are you sure you know
what you're doing?</b>

506
00:42:37.377 --> 00:42:40.312
<b>[ Chuckles ]
I hope so.</b>

507
00:42:40.380 --> 00:42:43.975
<b>Listen. be careful.</b>

508
00:42:50.057 --> 00:42:54.619
<b>- I know the way. Franjean.
- You always think you know the way.</b>

509
00:42:54.695 --> 00:42:58.153
<b>-I am the leader!
- How long will it take to find Raziel?</b>

510
00:42:58.232 --> 00:43:02.726
<b>Um. not long. She's been exiled
to an island just over those hills.</b>

511
00:43:02.803 --> 00:43:05.897
<b>- She's what?
- Exiled...</b>

512
00:43:05.973 --> 00:43:09.807
<b>by the evil Queen Bavmorda.
[ Laughs ]</b>

513
00:43:09.877 --> 00:43:12.505
<b>Rool. you fool. He does
not need to know everything.</b>

514
00:43:12.579 --> 00:43:15.173
<b>- I didn't tell him everything.
- You told him enough.</b>

515
00:43:15.249 --> 00:43:17.547
<b>- You mentioned the island. the queen.
- Wait a minute.</b>

516
00:43:17.618 --> 00:43:20.280
<b>[ Yelling ]
So?</b>

517
00:43:20.354 --> 00:43:23.152
<b>What do you mean? What are
you saying. mysterious island?</b>

518
00:43:23.223 --> 00:43:25.851
<b>Don't play with that wand.</b>

519
00:43:25.926 --> 00:43:28.486
<b>Cherlindrea told you
it holds vast powers.</b>

520
00:43:28.562 --> 00:43:31.053
<b>Only a great sorcerer can use it.</b>

521
00:43:31.131 --> 00:43:33.861
<b>-not a stupid peck like you.
-[ Laughing ]</b>

522
00:43:33.934 --> 00:43:37.097
<b>- This way.
- No. No. No. I don't think so.</b>

523
00:43:37.171 --> 00:43:39.469
<b>- All right. then this way.
- Eh. nope.</b>

524
00:43:39.540 --> 00:43:42.065
<b>- This way.
- This way?</b>

525
00:43:42.142 --> 00:43:45.873
<b>- That's what I said.
- This way.</b>

526
00:43:45.946 --> 00:43:49.404
<b>- You know where you're going?
- Of course.</b>

527
00:43:49.483 --> 00:43:52.179
<b>With us as your guides
no harm with befall you.</b>

528
00:43:52.252 --> 00:43:56.552
<b>-[ Thunder Rumbling ]
- [ Humming ]</b>

529
00:44:02.596 --> 00:44:06.794
<b>- [ Fussing ]
- Take it up!</b>

530
00:44:08.268 --> 00:44:12.534
<b>- We are not going in there!
- But Elora needs fresh milk.</b>

531
00:44:12.606 --> 00:44:17.475
<b>- And we are drenched.
- You are not in command. shorty. I am!</b>

532
00:44:17.544 --> 00:44:21.139
<b>- You hear me?
- Whoa!</b>

533
00:44:30.087 --> 00:44:32.453
<b>[ Glass Breaking.
Crowd Yelling ]</b>

534
00:44:44.301 --> 00:44:46.235
<b>[ Laughing ]</b>

535
00:44:58.849 --> 00:45:01.317
<b>- Excuse me? Excuse me.
- [ Laughing ]</b>

536
00:45:01.385 --> 00:45:04.354
<b>Could you spare some milk
for this poor. hungry baby?</b>

537
00:45:04.421 --> 00:45:06.286
<b>Get out of here. peck!</b>

538
00:45:06.357 --> 00:45:08.723
<b>Get outta here
or we'll cook ya!</b>

539
00:45:20.104 --> 00:45:22.038
<b>[ Cooing ]</b>

540
00:45:22.106 --> 00:45:26.008
<b>[ Rool ]
Ooh. look at her!</b>

541
00:45:26.076 --> 00:45:28.340
<b>I could use
a love potion on her!</b>

542
00:45:28.412 --> 00:45:32.246
<b>Franjean! Hey! Give me that
dust of broken heart.</b>

543
00:45:32.316 --> 00:45:34.045
<b>- Come on! Give it to me!
- Let go of me!</b>

544
00:45:34.118 --> 00:45:37.485
<b>It's very dangerous.
It belongs to the fairies!</b>

545
00:45:37.554 --> 00:45:39.579
<b>[ Growls. Sneezes ]</b>

546
00:45:39.657 --> 00:45:41.591
<b>- [ Yells ]
- [ Thumps ]</b>

547
00:45:41.659 --> 00:45:43.684
<b>Hey. quiet!
You want to get us killed?</b>

548
00:45:46.697 --> 00:45:50.565
<b>- [ Sneezes ]
- [ Grunts ]</b>

549
00:45:50.634 --> 00:45:54.400
<b>[ Franjean ] Oh. Rool! Always playing
with those fairy love potions.</b>

550
00:45:54.471 --> 00:45:56.598
<b>[ Meowing ]</b>

551
00:45:56.674 --> 00:46:01.805
<b>[ Sighing Deeply ]
You are so beautiful!</b>

552
00:46:01.879 --> 00:46:05.542
<b>-[ Meows ]
- Your eyes! Your whiskers!</b>

553
00:46:05.616 --> 00:46:08.244
<b>- I have to kiss you!
-Rool!</b>

554
00:46:08.319 --> 00:46:10.082
<b>That dust of broken heart!</b>

555
00:46:10.154 --> 00:46:12.088
<b>- [ Meows ]
- [ Rool Screams ]</b>

556
00:46:14.858 --> 00:46:17.759
<b>[ Panting. Grunting ]</b>

557
00:46:24.935 --> 00:46:27.130
<b>Beer!
[ Laughing ]</b>

558
00:46:30.274 --> 00:46:32.367
<b>These people are crazy!
This could be bad!</b>

559
00:46:36.947 --> 00:46:38.972
<b>[ Woman ]
Hurry! Hurry!</b>

560
00:46:39.049 --> 00:46:40.949
<b>My husband's coming!</b>

561
00:46:41.018 --> 00:46:43.043
<b>If he catches you here.
he'll kill us both!</b>

562
00:46:43.120 --> 00:46:45.748
<b>- How do I look?
- Not you!</b>

563
00:46:46.957 --> 00:46:48.891
<b>Where the hell
did you come from?</b>

564
00:46:48.959 --> 00:46:51.223
<b>I knew I shouldn't
have trusted you.</b>

565
00:46:51.295 --> 00:46:55.129
<b>Don't I know you?
I stole the baby from you. Daikini.</b>

566
00:46:55.199 --> 00:46:57.394
<b>- while you were taking a pee-pee!
- Cover your face!</b>

567
00:46:57.468 --> 00:47:01.097
<b>- You are crawling with Brownies.
- [ Shrieks ] I hate Brownies!</b>

568
00:47:01.171 --> 00:47:04.004
<b>[ Franjean. Laughing ]
Whoa!</b>

569
00:47:04.074 --> 00:47:06.668
<b>- Where is he? Where?
- [ Woman ] Hello. dear.</b>

570
00:47:06.744 --> 00:47:09.110
<b>There's nobody here but
me and. uh. my. uh--</b>

571
00:47:09.179 --> 00:47:11.579
<b>- I'll kill him!
- ...my cousin. Hilda.</b>

572
00:47:11.648 --> 00:47:13.912
<b>- Hilda?
- [ Woman ] Hilda.</b>

573
00:47:13.984 --> 00:47:16.111
<b>- Oh. Hilda!
- This is my husband. Llug.</b>

574
00:47:16.186 --> 00:47:18.916
<b>- Mm. Big husband.
- [ Woman ] Yes.</b>

575
00:47:18.989 --> 00:47:20.854
<b>- How do you do?
- [ Laughing ]</b>

576
00:47:20.924 --> 00:47:23.290
<b>[ Llug ]
Hilda! Ooh.</b>

577
00:47:23.360 --> 00:47:25.487
<b>Come on. girly.
Don't be shy.</b>

578
00:47:25.562 --> 00:47:28.190
<b>- Hey! Give her back!
- [ Coos ]</b>

579
00:47:28.265 --> 00:47:30.665
<b>- Pecks make terrible nursemaids.
- Nursemaid?</b>

580
00:47:30.734 --> 00:47:33.635
<b>- They get too excited.
- [ Grunts ]</b>

581
00:47:33.704 --> 00:47:36.332
<b>Excuse me!
Are we having a party?</b>

582
00:47:36.407 --> 00:47:38.432
<b>- Huh?
- Hey. hey. hey. hey!</b>

583
00:47:38.509 --> 00:47:43.173
<b>- [ Laughing Lewdly ]
- Stop. please. Ooh.</b>

584
00:47:43.247 --> 00:47:45.112
<b>Come on.
Fight like a man!</b>

585
00:47:45.182 --> 00:47:48.208
<b>- [ Grunts ]
- Want to breed?</b>

586
00:47:48.285 --> 00:47:51.311
<b>Tempting. but no.</b>

587
00:47:51.388 --> 00:47:54.152
<b>[ Growling ]</b>

588
00:47:54.224 --> 00:47:56.158
<b>Thank you.
Time to leave.</b>

589
00:47:56.226 --> 00:47:58.160
<b>- Bye. Hilda!
- [ Soldier] Take them out.</b>

590
00:47:58.228 --> 00:48:01.391
<b>- [ All. Gasping ]
- Hey! Come along!</b>

591
00:48:01.465 --> 00:48:04.059
<b>- [ Mad-Martigan ] Careful. you lout!
- Move along!</b>

592
00:48:04.134 --> 00:48:06.864
<b>[ Soldier ]
Gather up all these babies.</b>

593
00:48:06.937 --> 00:48:09.201
<b>[ Sorsha ] That baby over there.
Let me see its arm.</b>

594
00:48:12.943 --> 00:48:15.070
<b>That's not the one.</b>

595
00:48:18.782 --> 00:48:21.546
<b>You! Are you the mother
of that child?</b>

596
00:48:21.618 --> 00:48:24.212
<b>- [ In Woman's Voice ] Yes. Yes. I am.
- Let me see it.</b>

597
00:48:24.288 --> 00:48:25.880
<b>No! Don't let her!</b>

598
00:48:25.956 --> 00:48:27.423
<b>Aah!</b>

599
00:48:27.491 --> 00:48:30.358
<b>I gave you an order. woman!</b>

600
00:48:30.427 --> 00:48:32.224
<b>[ Grunts ]</b>

601
00:48:39.703 --> 00:48:43.195
<b>You--
You're... beautiful.</b>

602
00:48:43.273 --> 00:48:46.606
<b>- And you're very strong.
- Thank you.</b>

603
00:48:46.677 --> 00:48:49.111
<b>[ Chattering ]</b>

604
00:48:49.179 --> 00:48:51.670
<b>You're no woman!</b>

605
00:48:51.748 --> 00:48:53.613
<b>- Now. honey. take it easy.
- [ Llug ] Not a woman?</b>

606
00:48:53.684 --> 00:48:56.551
<b>- Gentlemen.
- Not a woman?</b>

607
00:48:56.620 --> 00:48:59.418
<b>- Meet Llug.
- [ Llug Yelling. Screaming ]</b>

608
00:49:00.691 --> 00:49:02.750
<b>- After them!
- Out of the way!</b>

609
00:49:09.032 --> 00:49:10.279
<b>- To the horses!
- [ Groans ]</b>

610
00:49:10.279 --> 00:49:11.371
<b>- To the horses!
- [ Groans ]</b>

611
00:49:13.916 --> 00:49:16.384
<b>[ Man ]
Hey! What are you doing?</b>

612
00:49:16.452 --> 00:49:19.353
<b>[ Yelling ]</b>

613
00:49:20.757 --> 00:49:22.691
<b>- Hyah!
- [ Neighing ]</b>

614
00:49:22.759 --> 00:49:26.661
<b>Mad-Martigan!
Mad-Martigan! Wait!</b>

615
00:49:27.664 --> 00:49:30.064
<b>[ Grunting. Groaning ]</b>

616
00:49:30.133 --> 00:49:35.036
<b>- He's not a woman!
- To your horses! Hyah! Hyah!</b>

617
00:49:35.104 --> 00:49:37.470
<b>Don't let them get away!</b>

618
00:49:39.142 --> 00:49:42.578
<b>- Mad-Martigan. stop!
- What?</b>

619
00:49:45.815 --> 00:49:51.185
<b>- [ Whimpering ]
- [ Grunting. Groaning ]</b>

620
00:49:54.357 --> 00:49:56.416
<b>Hyah!</b>

621
00:50:01.531 --> 00:50:04.056
<b>Mad-Martigan.
I'm warning you--</b>

622
00:50:06.102 --> 00:50:09.765
<b>- Ow!
- Prepare to die!</b>

623
00:50:33.162 --> 00:50:35.494
<b>Mad-Martigan!
Stop!</b>

624
00:50:51.514 --> 00:50:54.677
<b>[ Retching ]</b>

625
00:51:00.590 --> 00:51:03.024
<b>[ Gasps ]</b>

626
00:51:05.561 --> 00:51:07.620
<b>Franjean. help me!</b>

627
00:51:12.235 --> 00:51:14.169
<b>- Rool!
- Help!</b>

628
00:51:14.237 --> 00:51:17.297
<b>Rool! Rool.</b>

629
00:51:18.474 --> 00:51:22.274
<b>- Rool! What are you doing?
- Help me!</b>

630
00:51:27.617 --> 00:51:29.881
<b>- Come on. I am.
- Pull me in.</b>

631
00:51:29.952 --> 00:51:32.443
<b>[ Rool ]
Yeah. pull!</b>

632
00:51:32.522 --> 00:51:34.717
<b>[ Neighing ]</b>

633
00:51:44.433 --> 00:51:46.458
<b>[ Chuckling ]</b>

634
00:51:50.606 --> 00:51:52.631
<b>You can't have her!</b>

635
00:51:58.548 --> 00:52:00.243
<b>Whoa!
[ Grunts ]</b>

636
00:52:04.954 --> 00:52:08.549
<b>- [ Grunting ]
- Rool. this isn't funny!</b>

637
00:52:08.624 --> 00:52:10.558
<b>Help me cut the rope!</b>

638
00:52:23.739 --> 00:52:26.503
<b>Who-oa!</b>

639
00:52:26.576 --> 00:52:28.737
<b>[ Laughing. Cheering ]</b>

640
00:52:47.997 --> 00:52:50.591
<b>[ Mad-Martigan ]
Willow. stay down!</b>

641
00:52:54.303 --> 00:52:56.328
<b>Whoa!</b>

642
00:52:56.405 --> 00:52:58.635
<b>Whoa!</b>

643
00:52:58.708 --> 00:53:00.642
<b>Gone crazy?</b>

644
00:53:00.710 --> 00:53:02.871
<b>[ Willow ] You can't chase around
with Elora like this.</b>

645
00:53:02.945 --> 00:53:05.345
<b>- We're getting off!.
- Hyah!</b>

646
00:53:05.414 --> 00:53:08.042
<b>Oh! Hold on! Hyah!</b>

647
00:53:30.840 --> 00:53:33.329
<b>Whoa! Whoa!</b>

648
00:53:33.463 --> 00:53:36.455
<b>[ Grunting. Groaning ]</b>

649
00:53:36.533 --> 00:53:38.865
<b>- Oh. Rool.
- [ Grunts ]</b>

650
00:53:38.935 --> 00:53:42.598
<b>Now we stop. peck.</b>

651
00:53:42.672 --> 00:53:47.974
<b>Stupid Daikini.
Ask him to stop the wagon.</b>

652
00:53:48.044 --> 00:53:52.242
<b>Mad-Martigan! You never. ever
drive that fast with an infant!</b>

653
00:53:53.717 --> 00:53:56.242
<b>I just saved that infant's life!</b>

654
00:53:57.721 --> 00:54:00.053
<b>Hah! Hah!</b>

655
00:54:00.123 --> 00:54:02.057
<b>[ Franjean ]
Gather your wits. Come on.</b>

656
00:54:02.125 --> 00:54:05.151
<b>- [ Rool ] Don't worry about me.
-Come on!</b>

657
00:54:06.229 --> 00:54:08.424
<b>-[ Hoofbeats ]
- Get down!</b>

658
00:54:08.498 --> 00:54:10.898
<b>Uh. where am I?
Oh!</b>

659
00:54:12.802 --> 00:54:14.895
<b>Rool. you fool.
get out of the road!</b>

660
00:54:14.971 --> 00:54:19.340
<b>[ Groans. Grunts ]</b>

661
00:54:31.387 --> 00:54:33.981
<b>-[ Rool ] Ah. Franjean!
- You better clear out. Willow.</b>

662
00:54:34.057 --> 00:54:35.524
<b>Before those troops come back.</b>

663
00:54:35.592 --> 00:54:39.028
<b>- [ Rool ] Ah. my head!
- We don't need him. Elora.</b>

664
00:54:39.095 --> 00:54:42.292
<b>[ Crying ]</b>

665
00:54:47.437 --> 00:54:49.530
<b>[ Willow ]
Mad-Martigan. wait!</b>

666
00:54:49.606 --> 00:54:52.939
<b>Go home. Willow!
It's a dangerous world.</b>

667
00:54:53.009 --> 00:54:54.977
<b>Yeah. and that's why
we need your help.</b>

668
00:54:55.044 --> 00:54:58.275
<b>My help? [ Scoffs ]
What do you need my help for?</b>

669
00:54:58.348 --> 00:55:00.509
<b>You're a sorcerer!</b>

670
00:55:00.583 --> 00:55:03.814
<b>You're a great warrior.
and a swordsman.</b>

671
00:55:03.887 --> 00:55:06.788
<b>And you're ten times
bigger than I am. stupid!</b>

672
00:55:06.856 --> 00:55:10.121
<b>Are you trying to make my life
more difficult than it already is?</b>

673
00:55:10.193 --> 00:55:13.287
<b>-[ Dogs Barking ]
- [ Gasps ]</b>

674
00:55:13.363 --> 00:55:18.300
<b>- [ Barking Continues ]
- Hurry! Big dogs!</b>

675
00:55:18.368 --> 00:55:22.600
<b>Look. I'm sorry
I got angry.</b>

676
00:55:22.672 --> 00:55:24.640
<b>We wouldn't have
escaped without you.</b>

677
00:55:25.708 --> 00:55:27.539
<b>[ Cooing ]</b>

678
00:55:38.822 --> 00:55:41.655
<b>Well. don't expect me
to help you again.</b>

679
00:55:43.126 --> 00:55:46.755
<b>Good! Then we go that way!
To the lake!</b>

680
00:55:47.831 --> 00:55:50.959
<b>That way.</b>

681
00:55:51.034 --> 00:55:54.663
<b>You are drunk. and when you
are drunk you forget that...</b>

682
00:55:54.737 --> 00:55:56.671
<b>- I am in charge!
- You are in charge.</b>

683
00:55:56.739 --> 00:55:58.934
<b>Fine.
Then which way do we go?</b>

684
00:55:59.008 --> 00:56:01.033
<b>[ Together]
That way!</b>

685
00:56:01.110 --> 00:56:04.011
<b>[ Crow Cawing ]</b>

686
00:56:04.080 --> 00:56:08.608
<b>Oh. no!
That's the way I'm going.</b>

687
00:56:08.685 --> 00:56:11.677
<b>All right. all right. You can
follow me as far as the lake.</b>

688
00:56:11.754 --> 00:56:13.949
<b>But that's it!</b>

689
00:56:14.023 --> 00:56:17.789
<b>- You're not going south. are you?
- No. just as far as the lake.</b>

690
00:56:17.861 --> 00:56:23.026
<b>Good. Mumbo.Jumbo. I am hungry.
Go and get me some eggs or something.</b>

691
00:56:23.099 --> 00:56:25.727
<b>- We are not afraid of you!
- Now!</b>

692
00:56:25.802 --> 00:56:27.736
<b>[ Shrieking ]</b>

693
00:56:32.442 --> 00:56:37.106
<b>Kael. have you found the child?</b>

694
00:56:37.180 --> 00:56:38.943
<b>The search goes on. my queen.</b>

695
00:56:40.016 --> 00:56:42.041
<b>Why. with my powers.</b>

696
00:56:42.118 --> 00:56:45.315
<b>with the strength
of my great army.</b>

697
00:56:45.388 --> 00:56:48.824
<b>can you not find
one little child?</b>

698
00:56:48.892 --> 00:56:51.224
<b>We look even now.
It won't be long.</b>

699
00:56:51.294 --> 00:56:54.661
<b>Find the child.
Find the child!</b>

700
00:56:54.731 --> 00:56:57.325
<b>Time is running out.</b>

701
00:57:01.504 --> 00:57:05.907
<b>- [ Cooing ]
- Good night.</b>

702
00:57:05.975 --> 00:57:09.308
<b>She is kinda cute.</b>

703
00:57:09.379 --> 00:57:11.142
<b>When she's quiet.</b>

704
00:57:12.548 --> 00:57:14.482
<b>She's really a princess.</b>

705
00:57:14.550 --> 00:57:18.577
<b>Really?
And you're a great sorcerer.</b>

706
00:57:18.655 --> 00:57:20.589
<b>And I'm the king of Cashmere.</b>

707
00:57:20.657 --> 00:57:24.457
<b>Go to sleep. Willow.</b>

708
00:57:24.527 --> 00:57:27.018
<b>Good night. Mad-Martigan.</b>

709
00:57:27.096 --> 00:57:30.065
<b>[ Rool ]
Rats! Big rats! Rats!</b>

710
00:57:30.133 --> 00:57:33.466
<b>Uh-- Uh! Oh!
Rats! Ra--</b>

711
00:57:33.536 --> 00:57:36.437
<b>Oh. Rool. you had
that stupid rat dream!</b>

712
00:57:36.506 --> 00:57:38.440
<b>- [ Scoffs ]
- [ Whines ]</b>

713
00:57:47.250 --> 00:57:49.980
<b>Tuatha...</b>

714
00:57:50.053 --> 00:57:52.214
<b>Lawkathok...</b>

715
00:57:52.288 --> 00:57:54.222
<b>- Tuatha!
- [ Screams ]</b>

716
00:57:54.290 --> 00:57:57.020
<b>Huh?
Willow?</b>

717
00:57:58.094 --> 00:58:00.221
<b>Willow?</b>

718
00:58:01.998 --> 00:58:04.466
<b>Oh. [ Yawning ]
There you are.</b>

719
00:58:04.534 --> 00:58:06.502
<b>Mad-Martigan!</b>

720
00:58:06.569 --> 00:58:09.902
<b>[ Yawning ]
'Night. Willow.</b>

721
00:58:17.180 --> 00:58:19.580
<b>[ Birds Crying ]</b>

722
00:58:22.018 --> 00:58:24.009
<b>[ Rool ]
This way! This way!</b>

723
00:58:35.832 --> 00:58:37.766
<b>What are you doing?</b>

724
00:58:37.834 --> 00:58:40.200
<b>I found some blackroot.
She loves it!</b>

725
00:58:40.269 --> 00:58:43.204
<b>Blackroot? I am
the father of two children.</b>

726
00:58:43.272 --> 00:58:45.302
<b>and you never. ever
give a baby blackroot.</b>

727
00:58:45.436 --> 00:58:48.496
<b>Well. my mother
raised us on blackroot.</b>

728
00:58:48.572 --> 00:58:51.132
<b>It's good for ya!
It puts hair on your chest.</b>

729
00:58:51.208 --> 00:58:53.938
<b>- Doesn't it. Sticks?
- Her name is not Sticks.</b>

730
00:58:54.011 --> 00:58:56.946
<b>She's Elora Danan.
the future empress of Tir-Asleen.</b>

731
00:58:57.014 --> 00:58:59.346
<b>And the last thing she's gonna
want is a hairy chest!</b>

732
00:59:00.418 --> 00:59:02.409
<b>[ Elora Whimpering ]</b>

733
00:59:03.521 --> 00:59:05.546
<b>Did you see what he did?</b>

734
00:59:05.623 --> 00:59:08.888
<b>He stole our blackroot. I'll get
some more. don't worry about it.</b>

735
00:59:13.731 --> 00:59:17.064
<b>- There it is! The island!
- [ Laughing ]</b>

736
00:59:19.270 --> 00:59:21.204
<b>We made it.</b>

737
00:59:21.272 --> 00:59:25.834
<b>[ Franjean ] We have led you to
the island of the sorceress Fin Raziel.</b>

738
00:59:25.910 --> 00:59:30.176
<b>- We'll get a boat in that village.
- A big boat. [ Chuckles ]</b>

739
00:59:48.232 --> 00:59:50.223
<b>Well. looks like
I got you here.</b>

740
00:59:50.301 --> 00:59:52.769
<b>You!
What did you do?</b>

741
00:59:52.837 --> 00:59:55.863
<b>All you did was hang around
and eat our eggs! Huh?</b>

742
00:59:55.940 --> 00:59:57.908
<b>I found a boat.
We're all set.</b>

743
00:59:57.975 --> 01:00:01.911
<b>Good. Take these two lizards
out and drown them.</b>

744
01:00:01.979 --> 01:00:05.312
<b>- Who are you calling lizards?
- Heh? Heh?</b>

745
01:00:05.382 --> 01:00:07.350
<b>[ Growling. Yapping ]</b>

746
01:00:07.418 --> 01:00:10.080
<b>[ Franjean ]
Your mother was a lizard!</b>

747
01:00:13.057 --> 01:00:15.582
<b>- Good-bye. Sticks.
- [ Fussing ]</b>

748
01:00:18.262 --> 01:00:21.163
<b>If you really are a princess.</b>

749
01:00:21.232 --> 01:00:24.224
<b>take care of him.</b>

750
01:00:30.574 --> 01:00:33.839
<b>- Mad-Martigan!
- What?</b>

751
01:00:33.911 --> 01:00:35.811
<b>Thanks.</b>

752
01:00:45.322 --> 01:00:47.847
<b>Hey! Aah!
[ Spitting Sand ]</b>

753
01:00:47.925 --> 01:00:51.258
<b>-[ Rool ] Keep walkin; hero!
- Don't even turn around!</b>

754
01:00:52.463 --> 01:00:55.455
<b>- [ Cries ]
- It's all right. Elora.</b>

755
01:00:55.533 --> 01:00:57.967
<b>- Go to sleep.
- [ Thunder Rolling ]</b>

756
01:00:58.035 --> 01:01:00.367
<b>- Nobody'll find you here.
- [ Elora Fretting ]</b>

757
01:01:00.437 --> 01:01:02.029
<b>I'll be back with
Fin Raziel very soon.</b>

758
01:01:02.106 --> 01:01:05.439
<b>We will guard her
with our meager lives.</b>

759
01:01:05.509 --> 01:01:06.744
<b>[ Distant Thunder Continues ]</b>

760
01:01:06.744 --> 01:01:09.304
<b>[ Distant Thunder Continues ]</b>

761
01:01:33.737 --> 01:01:36.570
<b>Raziel!</b>

762
01:01:36.640 --> 01:01:40.474
<b>Fin Raziel!
I have to talk to you. please!</b>

763
01:01:44.381 --> 01:01:46.975
<b>Raziel!</b>

764
01:01:51.822 --> 01:01:55.485
<b>She's not here.</b>

765
01:01:58.462 --> 01:02:00.396
<b>- [ Screeching ]
- Aah!</b>

766
01:02:00.464 --> 01:02:04.025
<b>[ High. Squeaky Voice ]
Get back! Who are you?</b>

767
01:02:05.135 --> 01:02:08.036
<b>Who are you?</b>

768
01:02:10.441 --> 01:02:13.535
<b>- I'm Willow Ufgood.
- What are you doing here?</b>

769
01:02:13.611 --> 01:02:17.274
<b>I've come to find the great
sorceress. Fin Raziel.</b>

770
01:02:17.348 --> 01:02:19.942
<b>That's me!
I'm Raziel!</b>

771
01:02:21.986 --> 01:02:23.920
<b>This can't be right!</b>

772
01:02:23.988 --> 01:02:27.515
<b>One of Bavmorda's spells
transformed me.</b>

773
01:02:29.793 --> 01:02:32.387
<b>Believe me. it could
have been worse!</b>

774
01:02:32.463 --> 01:02:38.265
<b>Oh. Well. this wand is for you.
It's from Cherlindrea.</b>

775
01:02:38.335 --> 01:02:42.863
<b>Then the prophecy is true.
The princess has been born.</b>

776
01:02:42.940 --> 01:02:44.908
<b>Take me to her.</b>

777
01:02:47.444 --> 01:02:50.208
<b>It is Elora Danan.</b>

778
01:02:50.281 --> 01:02:53.216
<b>Isn't she beautiful?
[ Chuckling ]</b>

779
01:02:53.284 --> 01:02:56.253
<b>Isn't she beautiful?</b>

780
01:02:56.320 --> 01:02:59.812
<b>- That's Raziel?
- I don't know. I--</b>

781
01:02:59.890 --> 01:03:02.154
<b>I expected something
more grand. Less. uh--</b>

782
01:03:02.226 --> 01:03:04.160
<b>- Fuzzy.
- Fuzzy!</b>

783
01:03:04.228 --> 01:03:08.062
<b>You must use the wand.
Turn me back into my human form.</b>

784
01:03:08.132 --> 01:03:11.484
<b>- What do I do?
- You mean you're not a sorcerer?</b>

785
01:03:12.686 --> 01:03:15.177
<b>Yes. Sorta.</b>

786
01:03:15.255 --> 01:03:17.780
<b>-I'm a farmer.
- [ Sighing In Disgust ]</b>

787
01:03:17.858 --> 01:03:19.758
<b>But I do know a few tricks.</b>

788
01:03:19.826 --> 01:03:25.356
<b>Tricks? Cherlindrea sent you?
You must learn real magic.</b>

789
01:03:25.489 --> 01:03:29.516
<b>-[ Whinnying ]
- Horses! Horses!</b>

790
01:03:29.594 --> 01:03:32.119
<b>[ Raziel ] Quick! Take her!
Hurry! Hurry!</b>

791
01:03:32.196 --> 01:03:34.130
<b>[ Gasps ]</b>

792
01:03:40.924 --> 01:03:43.893
<b>[ Franjean ]
I knew he was a traitor!</b>

793
01:03:46.463 --> 01:03:49.159
<b>- Sorry about this. peck.
- Keep your mouth shut!</b>

794
01:03:50.234 --> 01:03:52.998
<b>Told you we'd find him
without your help.</b>

795
01:03:53.070 --> 01:03:55.038
<b>- Give me that baby.
- No!</b>

796
01:03:55.105 --> 01:03:58.438
<b>[ Elora Crying ]</b>

797
01:03:58.509 --> 01:04:02.468
<b>- Give her back!
- Leave me alone! Don't touch me!</b>

798
01:04:08.385 --> 01:04:10.285
<b>This is the one
we're looking for.</b>

799
01:04:10.354 --> 01:04:13.755
<b>- We must take it back to Nockmaar.
- [ Chittering ]</b>

800
01:04:16.527 --> 01:04:18.461
<b>Lose your skirt?</b>

801
01:04:26.136 --> 01:04:28.070
<b>I've still got what counts.</b>

802
01:04:28.138 --> 01:04:30.470
<b>Not for long.</b>

803
01:04:36.313 --> 01:04:39.840
<b>- Bring him.
- Over here!</b>

804
01:04:39.917 --> 01:04:41.851
<b>[ Grunting ]</b>

805
01:04:53.697 --> 01:04:56.461
<b>[ Panting. Grunting ]</b>

806
01:04:57.534 --> 01:05:00.264
<b>We'll never keep up
with those horses.</b>

807
01:05:00.337 --> 01:05:02.271
<b>Then we will
have to track them.</b>

808
01:05:02.339 --> 01:05:03.738
<b>That would take forever.</b>

809
01:05:03.807 --> 01:05:06.571
<b>Besides. even if we fine them.
they'll catch us.</b>

810
01:05:06.643 --> 01:05:09.840
<b>stick us in cages. torture us
and finally devour us.</b>

811
01:05:09.913 --> 01:05:11.881
<b>Are you suggesting
we go home?</b>

812
01:05:11.949 --> 01:05:14.884
<b>- Nah. This is more fun!
- All right.</b>

813
01:05:14.952 --> 01:05:16.886
<b>Fine. then.
Come on!</b>

814
01:05:17.921 --> 01:05:20.651
<b>[ Thunder Crashing ]</b>

815
01:05:23.393 --> 01:05:27.557
<b>[ Horse Neighing.
Elora Crying ]</b>

816
01:05:30.701 --> 01:05:34.137
<b>I'm worried about Elora.
She doesn't sound good.</b>

817
01:05:34.204 --> 01:05:36.968
<b>Hurry! Practice
the chant I taught you!</b>

818
01:05:37.040 --> 01:05:42.842
<b>- Tanna... looatha-- Oh. I can't
remember the middle part.</b>

819
01:05:42.913 --> 01:05:44.938
<b>Locktwaar!</b>

820
01:05:45.015 --> 01:05:48.007
<b>That's the word
that pleads for change.</b>

821
01:05:48.085 --> 01:05:50.019
<b>Locktwaar.</b>

822
01:05:53.724 --> 01:05:56.887
<b>Elora's cold and hungry.
She knows me.</b>

823
01:05:56.960 --> 01:05:58.894
<b>Please. let me
take care of her.</b>

824
01:05:58.962 --> 01:06:01.089
<b>I don't need help
from a peck.</b>

825
01:06:01.165 --> 01:06:04.760
<b>- [ Crying Continues ]
- [ Thunder Continues ]</b>

826
01:06:04.835 --> 01:06:08.896
<b>- What are you staring at?
- Your leg.</b>

827
01:06:08.972 --> 01:06:11.338
<b>I'd like to break it.</b>

828
01:06:11.408 --> 01:06:16.277
<b>You may find that difficult while
I'm up here and you're down there.</b>

829
01:06:19.383 --> 01:06:21.613
<b>I hate that woman.</b>

830
01:06:54.284 --> 01:06:56.343
<b>Hyah!</b>

831
01:07:00.157 --> 01:07:02.955
<b>- I found it. Kael.
- [ Elora Crying ]</b>

832
01:07:04.061 --> 01:07:07.121
<b>That should make
my mother happy.</b>

833
01:07:07.197 --> 01:07:10.223
<b>What are they gonna do to her?</b>

834
01:07:15.038 --> 01:07:17.336
<b>[ Dogs Howling ]</b>

835
01:07:17.407 --> 01:07:21.104
<b>[ Panting. Growling ]</b>

836
01:07:22.746 --> 01:07:25.442
<b>Hither walha...</b>

837
01:07:25.515 --> 01:07:29.042
<b>bairn deru bordak...</b>

838
01:07:29.119 --> 01:07:31.053
<b>- bellanockt.
- [ Sniffng ]</b>

839
01:07:31.121 --> 01:07:34.022
<b>[ Sniffng ] That's magic?
Smells terrible.</b>

840
01:07:34.091 --> 01:07:37.322
<b>- It's the life spark. It forms after--
- Well. it stinks!</b>

841
01:07:37.394 --> 01:07:40.557
<b>- This whole thing stinks!
- Ignore him. Willow.</b>

842
01:07:40.631 --> 01:07:43.657
<b>- He's a fool!
- If only I had a sword!</b>

843
01:07:43.734 --> 01:07:46.828
<b>- [ Grunting ]
- If only you'd quit talking about it.</b>

844
01:07:46.903 --> 01:07:50.270
<b>Willow. you must transform me
to my human self.</b>

845
01:07:50.340 --> 01:07:53.173
<b>But. Raziel.
I'm not ready yet.</b>

846
01:07:53.243 --> 01:07:56.474
<b>You'd better be.
Get me down.</b>

847
01:07:56.546 --> 01:08:00.004
<b>- [ Grunts ]
- [ Squeals ]</b>

848
01:08:00.083 --> 01:08:02.517
<b>Ow!
[ Groans ]</b>

849
01:08:05.122 --> 01:08:08.148
<b>Why don't you help me get out of here
instead of chattering with that muskrat?</b>

850
01:08:08.225 --> 01:08:10.955
<b>Muskrat!
When I change back...</b>

851
01:08:11.028 --> 01:08:14.987
<b>to my former self.
I will crush this army.</b>

852
01:08:15.065 --> 01:08:17.727
<b>and take Elora Danan
to Tir-Asleen...</b>

853
01:08:17.801 --> 01:08:20.395
<b>where she will be safe.</b>

854
01:08:20.470 --> 01:08:22.802
<b>- [ Chomping ]
- Ow!</b>

855
01:08:22.873 --> 01:08:24.807
<b>What'd you bite me for?</b>

856
01:08:24.875 --> 01:08:28.208
<b>You need three drops
of your blood to put in the potion.</b>

857
01:08:28.278 --> 01:08:31.577
<b>- Well. you coulda warned me.
- [ Scoffs ]</b>

858
01:08:31.648 --> 01:08:34.082
<b>For beginners.
there's some pain.</b>

859
01:08:34.151 --> 01:08:39.248
<b>but don't let anything
break your concentration.</b>

860
01:08:44.394 --> 01:08:47.261
<b>Hither greenan bairn
claideb lunanockt.</b>

861
01:08:47.331 --> 01:08:51.097
<b>- Hello. everybody! We have arrived!
- You are saved.</b>

862
01:08:51.168 --> 01:08:54.001
<b>- Shh!
- [ Raziel ] Don't interrupt.</b>

863
01:08:55.439 --> 01:08:58.602
<b>Hither greenan bairn
claideb lunanockt.</b>

864
01:08:58.675 --> 01:09:01.542
<b>What are you going
to look like if this works?</b>

865
01:09:01.611 --> 01:09:04.102
<b>- Don't interrupt.
- Sorry.</b>

866
01:09:04.181 --> 01:09:06.115
<b>Hither greenan bairn
claideb lunanockt.</b>

867
01:09:06.183 --> 01:09:09.516
<b>I am a young.
beautiful woman.</b>

868
01:09:09.586 --> 01:09:11.383
<b>Concentrate. Willow.</b>

869
01:09:11.455 --> 01:09:13.616
<b>Hither greenan bairn
claideb lunanockt.</b>

870
01:09:13.690 --> 01:09:16.090
<b>Hither greenan bairn
claideb lunanockt.</b>

871
01:09:16.159 --> 01:09:18.286
<b>No!
You're losing me!</b>

872
01:09:18.362 --> 01:09:21.798
<b>- [ Stretching Sound ]
-Hither greenan bairn claideb lunanockt.</b>

873
01:09:21.865 --> 01:09:23.389
<b>[ Whimpering ]</b>

874
01:09:24.768 --> 01:09:26.702
<b>Hither greenan bairn
claideb--</b>

875
01:09:26.770 --> 01:09:29.796
<b>- Aah! Aah!
- You all right? Nice try. Willow.</b>

876
01:09:29.873 --> 01:09:33.331
<b>[ Cawing ]</b>

877
01:09:37.848 --> 01:09:41.807
<b>Farmers!
Cherlindrea sends me farmers!</b>

878
01:09:41.885 --> 01:09:45.377
<b>Whew! The Nelwyn
really butchered that one.</b>

879
01:09:45.455 --> 01:09:47.391
<b>- I'm sorry. Raziel.
- You want out?</b>

880
01:09:47.391 --> 01:09:48.722
<b>- I'm sorry. Raziel.
- You want out?</b>

881
01:09:48.792 --> 01:09:51.727
<b>Easy. We can pick a lock.
Come on.</b>

882
01:09:51.795 --> 01:09:53.729
<b>No. No. no.
Like this!</b>

883
01:09:53.797 --> 01:09:55.731
<b>I know what I'm doing.
It's my spear. Leave it alone.</b>

884
01:09:55.799 --> 01:09:59.735
<b>Let me do it.
Out of the way. rodents.</b>

885
01:10:00.804 --> 01:10:02.601
<b>Take your hand off that.</b>

886
01:10:02.672 --> 01:10:07.132
<b>You leave that alone.
you stupid. fat Daikini!</b>

887
01:10:07.210 --> 01:10:08.837
<b>Ow!</b>

888
01:10:08.912 --> 01:10:11.005
<b>[ Laughing ]
Dust of broken hearts.</b>

889
01:10:12.215 --> 01:10:13.842
<b>[ Grunts ]</b>

890
01:10:15.619 --> 01:10:18.986
<b>[ Sighs Deeply ]</b>

891
01:10:19.055 --> 01:10:21.683
<b>[ Grunting ]</b>

892
01:10:21.758 --> 01:10:24.591
<b>Ha. ha!
You are free!</b>

893
01:10:24.661 --> 01:10:28.927
<b>Come on. Mad-Martigan.
Let's get Elora Danan out of here.</b>

894
01:10:28.999 --> 01:10:33.129
<b>- Yeah. It'll be fun.
- Come on!</b>

895
01:10:44.813 --> 01:10:48.840
<b>- Are you all right?
- Yeah.</b>

896
01:10:48.917 --> 01:10:51.010
<b>I feel... good.</b>

897
01:10:51.086 --> 01:10:54.647
<b>- The dust of broken hearts.
- Ah--</b>

898
01:10:54.723 --> 01:10:57.283
<b>Hey. come on!</b>

899
01:11:02.731 --> 01:11:05.859
<b>- [ Franjean ] Let me see!
- Let me see. You always see.</b>

900
01:11:05.934 --> 01:11:08.368
<b>There's Elora. right there.
on those furs.</b>

901
01:11:08.436 --> 01:11:10.700
<b>[ Fussing ]</b>

902
01:11:10.772 --> 01:11:12.933
<b>[ Franjean ]
Hey. wait! Leave this to us.</b>

903
01:11:13.008 --> 01:11:15.738
<b>- It's too dangerous for you.
- Only one of us should go in there.</b>

904
01:11:15.810 --> 01:11:18.643
<b>I've got experience in this
sort of thing. I know what I'm doing.</b>

905
01:11:45.940 --> 01:11:48.841
<b>[ Together]
Uh-oh.</b>

906
01:11:48.910 --> 01:11:52.846
<b>[ Whispering ]
Wait. Shh. No! No! Mad-M...--</b>

907
01:12:03.391 --> 01:12:06.224
<b>- I love you.
- [ Willow ] Mad-Martigan!</b>

908
01:12:06.294 --> 01:12:09.263
<b>- What are you doing?
- Take the baby and go! Come on!</b>

909
01:12:09.331 --> 01:12:11.265
<b>Come on!</b>

910
01:12:21.343 --> 01:12:23.538
<b>- Oh. Sorsha.
- Oh!</b>

911
01:12:23.611 --> 01:12:25.203
<b>[ Groaning ]</b>

912
01:12:25.280 --> 01:12:28.272
<b>Wake from
this hateful sleep.</b>

913
01:12:28.350 --> 01:12:30.750
<b>It deprives me
of your beauty.</b>

914
01:12:30.819 --> 01:12:34.778
<b>- The beauty of your eyes--
- One move. jackass.</b>

915
01:12:34.856 --> 01:12:37.256
<b>and you really
will be a woman.</b>

916
01:12:38.626 --> 01:12:42.585
<b>You are my sun!
My moon!</b>

917
01:12:42.664 --> 01:12:47.124
<b>My starlit sky.
Without you. I dwell in darkness.</b>

918
01:12:47.202 --> 01:12:51.298
<b>- I love you.
- What are you doing here?</b>

919
01:12:51.373 --> 01:12:54.706
<b>Your power has enchanted me.
I stand helpless against it.</b>

920
01:12:54.776 --> 01:12:56.710
<b>Come to me. now.</b>

921
01:12:56.778 --> 01:12:59.269
<b>Tonight. let me
worship you in my arms.</b>

922
01:12:59.347 --> 01:13:02.043
<b>- Get away from me!
- I love you!</b>

923
01:13:02.117 --> 01:13:04.585
<b>Stop saying that!</b>

924
01:13:04.652 --> 01:13:08.952
<b>How can I stop the beating of
my heart? It pounds like never before.</b>

925
01:13:09.023 --> 01:13:11.583
<b>- Out of fear.
- Out of love!</b>

926
01:13:11.659 --> 01:13:14.150
<b>I can stop it.
I'll kill you.</b>

927
01:13:14.229 --> 01:13:17.164
<b>Death. next to love.
is a trivial thing.</b>

928
01:13:19.968 --> 01:13:22.459
<b>Your touch is worth
1 00.000 deaths.</b>

929
01:13:25.707 --> 01:13:27.242
<b>- [ Elora Cries ]
- What goes on here?</b>

930
01:13:27.242 --> 01:13:28.334
<b>- [ Elora Cries ]
- What goes on here?</b>

931
01:13:34.015 --> 01:13:36.006
<b>Deceiver!</b>

932
01:13:37.585 --> 01:13:39.450
<b>[ Kael ]
Stop him!</b>

933
01:13:48.396 --> 01:13:51.024
<b>[ Kael ]
Captain. get up!</b>

934
01:13:51.099 --> 01:13:53.659
<b>[ Yelling ]</b>

935
01:14:01.443 --> 01:14:06.107
<b>- You are great.
- [ Chuckles. Grunts ]</b>

936
01:14:06.181 --> 01:14:09.048
<b>Get on that shield!</b>

937
01:14:17.091 --> 01:14:19.059
<b>[ Grunts ]</b>

938
01:14:20.428 --> 01:14:22.988
<b>Sorsha!</b>

939
01:14:25.633 --> 01:14:27.658
<b>After them!</b>

940
01:14:28.870 --> 01:14:31.737
<b>[ Groans. Screams ]</b>

941
01:14:34.409 --> 01:14:36.775
<b>- [ Barking. Growling ]
- Whoa! Hey!</b>

942
01:14:36.845 --> 01:14:39.109
<b>[ Screaming ]</b>

943
01:14:41.583 --> 01:14:43.517
<b>[ Man ]
They're getting away!</b>

944
01:14:52.360 --> 01:14:54.624
<b>-Follow me. Rool. I don't know.
- Where are you?</b>

945
01:14:54.696 --> 01:14:58.928
<b>- Aah! Ooh.
- Oh. no. where did everybody go?</b>

946
01:14:59.000 --> 01:15:00.934
<b>Maybe it was
something we said.</b>

947
01:15:07.809 --> 01:15:09.936
<b>[ Mad-Martigan Screams ]</b>

948
01:15:17.085 --> 01:15:20.953
<b>[ Both Screaming ]</b>

949
01:15:26.261 --> 01:15:28.388
<b>[ Moaning ]</b>

950
01:15:28.463 --> 01:15:30.522
<b>[ Moaning. Groaning ]</b>

951
01:15:30.598 --> 01:15:33.260
<b>[ Laughing ]</b>

952
01:15:54.989 --> 01:15:58.117
<b>Ohh-h-h-h!</b>

953
01:15:58.192 --> 01:16:00.251
<b>[ Screams ]</b>

954
01:16:01.329 --> 01:16:03.695
<b>[ Screams ]</b>

955
01:16:07.402 --> 01:16:09.461
<b>[ Clattering ]</b>

956
01:16:09.537 --> 01:16:12.768
<b>-[ Chickens Clucking ]
- [ Elora Giggling ]</b>

957
01:16:19.280 --> 01:16:21.305
<b>Mad-Martigan!</b>

958
01:16:38.099 --> 01:16:42.365
<b>- Mad-Martigan!
- What the hell happened up there?</b>

959
01:16:42.437 --> 01:16:44.837
<b>You started spouting poetry.</b>

960
01:16:44.906 --> 01:16:47.500
<b>- Poetry?
- Yeah.</b>

961
01:16:47.575 --> 01:16:50.840
<b>''I love you. Sorsha.
I worship you. Sorsha.''</b>

962
01:16:50.912 --> 01:16:52.846
<b>You almost got us killed!</b>

963
01:16:52.914 --> 01:16:54.848
<b>''I love you. Sorsha''?</b>

964
01:16:54.916 --> 01:16:57.350
<b>I don't love her.
She kicked me in the face.</b>

965
01:16:57.418 --> 01:17:00.819
<b>I hate her! Don't I?</b>

966
01:17:00.922 --> 01:17:02.947
<b>[ Cawing ]</b>

967
01:17:03.024 --> 01:17:05.458
<b>Kael! Kael!</b>

968
01:17:05.526 --> 01:17:08.188
<b>Nockmaar soldiers!</b>

969
01:17:10.164 --> 01:17:13.622
<b>[ Man ]
Hoy! Get the children! Come on!</b>

970
01:17:16.404 --> 01:17:18.338
<b>- Get the children!
- They're after us! We need to hide.</b>

971
01:17:18.406 --> 01:17:21.500
<b>Come on. Follow me. Quick!
Come on! Move!</b>

972
01:17:37.992 --> 01:17:39.766
<b>I knew you'd
get out of that rattrap.</b>

973
01:17:39.766 --> 01:17:40.698
<b>I knew you'd
get out of that rattrap.</b>

974
01:17:43.303 --> 01:17:45.237
<b>You left me to die. Airk.</b>

975
01:17:45.305 --> 01:17:46.499
<b>I probably saved your life.</b>

976
01:17:46.573 --> 01:17:48.598
<b>We were slaughtered
and I lost a lot of good--</b>

977
01:17:48.675 --> 01:17:51.007
<b>- Shh! Quiet!
- [ Horse Whinnying ]</b>

978
01:17:52.112 --> 01:17:54.046
<b>[ Kael ]
Tear this village apart!</b>

979
01:17:54.114 --> 01:17:58.517
<b>Look everywhere!
Find the child!</b>

980
01:18:04.291 --> 01:18:06.191
<b>[ Crying Lustily ]</b>

981
01:18:07.394 --> 01:18:10.852
<b>- [ Cawing. Imitating Baby ]
- Shh!</b>

982
01:18:16.703 --> 01:18:18.637
<b>Shh-shh-shh!</b>

983
01:18:18.705 --> 01:18:21.799
<b>[ Soldier's Voices
Above. Indistinct ]</b>

984
01:18:34.321 --> 01:18:37.347
<b>Tell Sorsha
I search the north bank!</b>

985
01:18:37.424 --> 01:18:39.358
<b>- Hah! Hah!
- Yes. General.</b>

986
01:18:52.472 --> 01:18:54.531
<b>- Quiet. Shh!
- [ Fretting ]</b>

987
01:19:11.191 --> 01:19:13.853
<b>[ Sorsha Screams. Grunts ]</b>

988
01:19:13.927 --> 01:19:16.919
<b>- Sorsha!
- Back.</b>

989
01:19:16.997 --> 01:19:18.692
<b>Back!</b>

990
01:19:25.372 --> 01:19:27.932
<b>Back!</b>

991
01:19:28.008 --> 01:19:32.274
<b>- Keep the baby quiet.
- She needs to be changed.</b>

992
01:19:32.346 --> 01:19:34.143
<b>- Nockmaar scum!
- You'll never defeat us.</b>

993
01:19:34.214 --> 01:19:36.045
<b>- Give up the baby!
- Shut up!</b>

994
01:19:38.018 --> 01:19:39.713
<b>What does Bavmorda want
with this baby. anyway?</b>

995
01:19:39.786 --> 01:19:41.549
<b>She's a princess.</b>

996
01:19:41.622 --> 01:19:43.453
<b>- We're taking her to Tir-Asleen.
- Tir-Asleen?</b>

997
01:19:43.523 --> 01:19:46.458
<b>Even if you could
find it. peck.</b>

998
01:19:46.526 --> 01:19:48.892
<b>she's right--you'd never
get past the Nockmaar army.</b>

999
01:19:48.962 --> 01:19:51.430
<b>There's an even bigger
army at Tir-Asleen.</b>

1000
01:19:51.498 --> 01:19:53.989
<b>- If we can just get there--
- [ Woman Screaming ]</b>

1001
01:19:57.404 --> 01:20:00.168
<b>I've lost more than half
my men fighting Bavmorda.</b>

1002
01:20:00.240 --> 01:20:02.834
<b>Now you and this peck
are gonna take her on?</b>

1003
01:20:02.909 --> 01:20:06.174
<b>You always told me you served
no one. Mad-Martigan.</b>

1004
01:20:06.246 --> 01:20:08.180
<b>Since when are
you a crusader?</b>

1005
01:20:10.484 --> 01:20:13.749
<b>He's not gonna help you. peck.</b>

1006
01:20:13.820 --> 01:20:15.811
<b>He's a worthless thief.</b>

1007
01:20:17.224 --> 01:20:19.658
<b>I'm not a thief. Airk.</b>

1008
01:20:19.726 --> 01:20:22.695
<b>He's not a thief.</b>

1009
01:20:22.763 --> 01:20:24.993
<b>Are you?</b>

1010
01:20:39.546 --> 01:20:43.380
<b>I serve the Nelwyn. Airk.</b>

1011
01:20:48.088 --> 01:20:50.682
<b>- Want to come with us?
- You'll never make it. Mad-Martigan.</b>

1012
01:20:52.626 --> 01:20:54.560
<b>Then once again
we say good-bye.</b>

1013
01:21:08.375 --> 01:21:11.811
<b>- Over here!
- Sorsha!</b>

1014
01:21:11.878 --> 01:21:15.245
<b>Weapons down or she's dead!</b>

1015
01:21:20.454 --> 01:21:22.183
<b>Hyah! Hyah!</b>

1016
01:21:27.794 --> 01:21:30.729
<b>- Hyah!
- Get to your horses! After 'em!</b>

1017
01:21:32.966 --> 01:21:34.900
<b>[ Screaming ]</b>

1018
01:22:16.910 --> 01:22:19.435
<b>This way!
This way!</b>

1019
01:22:19.513 --> 01:22:22.209
<b>As the crow flies. you fools!</b>

1020
01:22:29.089 --> 01:22:31.956
<b>- You're holding me too tight!
- I don't want you to get away.</b>

1021
01:22:32.025 --> 01:22:36.860
<b>Why? Because I'm your sun.
your moon. your starlit sky?</b>

1022
01:22:38.432 --> 01:22:40.662
<b>Get your hair out of my face.
or I'll chop it off.</b>

1023
01:22:44.504 --> 01:22:48.463
<b>Did I really-- Did I really
say those things last night?</b>

1024
01:22:48.542 --> 01:22:51.670
<b>- In your tent?
- You said you loved me.</b>

1025
01:22:51.745 --> 01:22:54.236
<b>- I don't remember that.
- You lied to me!</b>

1026
01:22:54.314 --> 01:22:56.714
<b>No. I--</b>

1027
01:22:56.783 --> 01:22:59.217
<b>I just wasn't myself
last night.</b>

1028
01:22:59.286 --> 01:23:03.655
<b>I suppose my power enchanted you.
and you were helpless against it.</b>

1029
01:23:03.723 --> 01:23:06.692
<b>- Um. sort of.
- Then what?</b>

1030
01:23:06.760 --> 01:23:08.853
<b>It went away.</b>

1031
01:23:08.929 --> 01:23:12.592
<b>It went away?
''I dwell in darkness without you.''</b>

1032
01:23:12.666 --> 01:23:14.759
<b>- and it went away?
- Yeah.</b>

1033
01:23:14.835 --> 01:23:16.803
<b>[ Grunts ]</b>

1034
01:23:18.905 --> 01:23:20.839
<b>[ Roars ]</b>

1035
01:23:20.907 --> 01:23:23.102
<b>- [ Shouts ]
- [ Grunts ]</b>

1036
01:23:25.879 --> 01:23:29.975
<b>- Whoa.
- [ Sorsha Panting ]</b>

1037
